beds, dining sets, office furniture, and more. Save big while upgrading your home with premium pieces.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","sortValue":0,"description":"Unlock great savings with Damro’s Offers page. From sofas and recliners to beds, dining sets, and storage solutions—you’ll find promotional deals across all categories. Don’t miss out on limited-time discounts and special bundles to enhance your home with quality furniture at unbeatable prices.\n\n","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/2.jpg","subcategory":[]},{"_id":"60b5da71a4604b0430f2bb9f","name":"Living","slug":"living","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Living Room Furniture | Sofas, Recliners, Tables | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/living\",\n  \"description\": \"Discover Damro’s wide range of living room furniture including sofas, recliners, coffee tables, and TV units – designed to elevate comfort and modern style.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","sortValue":2,"description":"Design your ideal living room with Damro’s versatile furniture collection. From plush fabric and leather sofas, recliners, and elegant center tables to stylish TV stands and entertainment units—our pieces blend comfort, style, and functionality to help you curate a welcoming and cohesive living space.\n\n","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/2 Sofas.jpg","subcategory":[{"_id":"60b5ddd3a4604b0430f2bbac","name":"Sofas","slug":"sofas","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/sofasicons.jpg","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/2 Sofas.jpg","description":"Create a welcoming and comfortable living area with Damro’s Sofa collection. Choose from plush fabric and genuine leather sofas, ergonomic recliners, stylish corner sectionals, and versatile sofa beds. Each sofa is crafted for elegance, durability, and comfort to fit diverse styles and space needs in modern homes.","homeCategorImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Sofas.jpg","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Sofas – Fabric, Leather \u0026 Sectionals | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/sofas\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s extensive sofa collection featuring premium fabric sofas, genuine leather sofas, recliners, and sectional units. Designed for style, comfort, and durability.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"60b5dfcea4604b0430f2bbad","name":"Fabric Sofas","description":"Revamp your living room with Damro’s Fabric Sofas. Choose from sleek 2‑seater, spacious 3‑seater, and cozy recliner fabric sofas featuring soft upholstery, sturdy frames, and contemporary styles. Designed for comfort and visual appeal, each fabric sofa brings a cozy, stylish touch to your home.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/fabric sofa.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b5ddd3a4604b0430f2bbac","ourcollection":true,"icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/fabric sofa.jpg","categoryImage":"","sortValue":0,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-28T16:04:54.219Z","__v":0,"slug":"fabric-sofas","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eAre you seeking a luxurious yet affordable fabric sofa to complete your living room? Damro, a trusted name in the furniture industry, offers a wide range of fabric sofas that blend comfort, style, and durability. With a focus on premium materials and a variety of designs to suit every taste and budget, Damro fabric sofas stand out as a top choice in India. Whether you're searching for a luxury sofa, a sleek modern sofa in India, or an elegant yet budget-friendly option, Damro delivers quality without compromise.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Go For a Fabric Sofa?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eMany reasons frame fabric sofas as one of the preferred choices for homeowners. They are quite comfortable with a wide range of styles and prices that make them affordable and suitable for nearly every living space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfort\u003c/strong\u003e: Compared to leather or wooden sofas, fabric sofas tend to be more comfortable. This is because the fabric upholstery is soft making it warm and welcoming, ideal for people that like lounging or having visitors over.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVariety of Designs\u003c/strong\u003e: Unlike the other types of couches, the fabric ones are available in very many designs, colours and patterns. Whether you are a fan of modern-day minimalistic designs, classic grandeur, or anything in between, such couches will have something for every design preference.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAffordability:\u003c/strong\u003e Contrary to that, leather and other expensive materials, there is a cost advantage with fabric sofas. You are able to acquire an adequately designed and comfortable sofa that does not cost an arm and a leg.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEase of Modifications:\u003c/strong\u003e You can find fabric sofas made from several types of fabrics including but not limited to linen, cotton, velvet and low-grade synthetic blends which give room for various touches and different effects.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTypes of Fabric Sofas\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eFabric couches are excellent investments; however, it is very important to understand how to choose the right fabric upholstery for couches. The upholstery fabric determines how the sofa looks and feels but also how long it will last and how easily it will be cleaned. Below are some of the fabrics that are commonly found in sofas:\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eDamro Offering Different Types of Fabric Sofa Sets\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric Sofa Set 3+2\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThis one has one 3-seater and one 2-seater and is perfect for a medium-sized living room. It fills up the space without making it seem overcrowded with enough seating as comfort is served along with style.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric Sofa Set 3+1+1\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt is one of the styles that can provide versatile seating style. The set includes one 3-seater sofa and two individual armchairs. It's apt for bigger-sized living rooms or when you want separate zones to be created in the living room.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3 Seater Fabric Sofa\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA 3-seater sofa is the perfect choice for small rooms, combining comfort and sophistication for that ideal centrepiece in small to medium living rooms paired well with accent chairs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric Sofa L-Shape\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eL-shaped sofas in fabric are a great opportunity to utilize available room space. They are both stylish and functional, so ideal for large rooms for families or those who like to entertain.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric Sofa Designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro's fabric sofa designs are versatile, so you can easily find the design that matches your traditional and modern aesthetic. You can choose from:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eA classic design has plush cushioning with neutral fabrics to provide a timeless look.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eA modern style with sleek lines, and bold colours for your modern homes.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eModular sofa designs offer you flexibility, which can easily be rearranged to fit into different spaces.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric Sofa Set Price\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro offers fabric sofa sets in a variety of price ranges. That way, something should suit one's budget.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eBudget Versions: From ₹28,000 to ₹30,000 for an average 3-seater or 3+1+1 model.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMid-range: ₹35,000 to ₹60,000 for more fashion-forward designs with increased comfort.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLuxury Fabric Sofas: Over ₹60,000 for premium materials, high-end design, and more collections.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eInfinite Range of Options for Your House\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eFabric sofas by Damro aim to satisfy the interests of different consumers by being available in a range of cuts from modern simple to classic sophisticated styles. The best part about Damro fabric sofas is that each one of them can be incorporated so well in a modern house as well as a blended ancient décor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eModern Sofas in India:\u003c/strong\u003e Damro's modern fabric sofas have clean lines, simple forms, and simple natural colours, making them ideal for modern apartments. Dressed in these designs, this style offers little effectiveness but much to please the eye. Ideal for city habitats, such sofas are aesthetically pleasing which is why they are preferred in modern homes even though they seem out of place practically.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTimeless Designs:\u003c/strong\u003e If you love classic designs and would consider buying distinctive pieces of furniture, look to Damros' traditional upholstery as they bring the beauty and style of classic pieces but with a modern take on them. Many of these sofas are defined by refined upholstery techniques, styling elements, and beautiful surfaces that welcome many textures inviting warm feelings.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDivan and Modular Varieties:\u003c/strong\u003e Family gatherings or a lot of guests at home do not pose a problem as it would be with the other types of fabric sofas that would normally restrict space, thanks to Damro sectional fabric sofas. The seating arrangement gives options to the users as to how best the seating will be arranged according to the available space. Modular options are also offered whereby you can select the different sections and configurations that best suit you encapsulated in a sofa cushion.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSofas for Small Houses:\u003c/strong\u003e Damro is aware of the situation and the trend in which people live these days as well- especially in smaller-sized houses and apartments such made shorter couches or fabric sofa sets are a necessity. Fabrics used in their portrait sofas range from soft fibres to the hard Cushiony ones incorporating intelligent designs that keep the modern loungers and their owners in mind.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSofa Fabric Catalogue with Price\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro provides a comprehensive sofa fabric catalogue that showcases the different fabric options available, including:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eCotton blends for breathability and comfort.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLinen fabrics for a more sophisticated, natural look.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMicrofiber for durability and easy cleaning.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eVelvet for a luxurious touch.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEach fabric option is priced differently, with prices typically rising for premium fabrics like velvet or microfiber. You can view the full fabric catalogue in Damro showrooms or on their official website.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to Choose the Perfect Fabric Sofa for Your Home\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eChoosing the right fabric sofa for your home involves several considerations:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eRoom Size: Ensure the sofa fits your living room dimensions without crowding the space.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eFabric Type: For homes with kids or pets, opt for durable, stain-resistant fabrics like microfiber. For a more luxurious feel, go for velvet or cotton blends.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eColour: Neutral tones can blend seamlessly into any décor, while bold colours make a statement.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eStyle: Decide whether you want a contemporary, minimalist design or something more classic and plush.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to take care of your fabric sofa\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you want your fabric sofa to last you for a long time, proper care and maintenance must be done. Here are some tips to keep your sofa looking fresh and clean:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVacuum Regularly:\u003c/strong\u003e Contrary to popular belief, dust and dirt do settle on the surface of the fabric sofa, so it's advisable that from time to time vacuum clean it using the soft brush attachment. This will prevent dirt build-up and enhance the general appearance of the sofa.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUse Fabric Protectors:\u003c/strong\u003e A fabric protector spray will help to prevent all kinds of spills and dirt. This is very helpful, especially for those families that have kids or pets.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpot Clean:\u003c/strong\u003e If you spill - blot it with a clean damp cloth immediately. Do not rub the fabric as it will only make the stain worse by spreading it around. For more hard-to-remove stains get some fabric cleaner or get in touch with a cleaning service.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRotate Cushions:\u003c/strong\u003e To avoid imbalanced wear and tear, make sure that you periodically swap your sofa cushions. This stops one side from getting more damaged than the other and also helps to preserve the design of the sofa.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBuy Fabric Sofa Online across India\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro makes it handy to shop from your home for fabric sofas by shopping through its website and any other online e-shopping facilities. With their delivery facilities across India, you can sit at home, surf through their collection, see the detailed product specifications, and place an order.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric Sofa Deals from Damro\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro often provides special sales and discounts on fabric sofa sets, especially during festival seasons and sale events. Catch the latest offers on their website or by subscribing to their newsletters.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCollection of Current Fabric Sofas\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro continues to update the latest fabric sofa designs in accordance with changing trends that abound in the market. Whether it's the minimalist, sleek models or even a more luxurious, plush sofa, you will be able to find the most updated styles that suit your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric Sofas for Living Room\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro sofas can greatly boost the style and comfort of your living room. From the traditional 3-seater to the L-shape sofa, Damro has various designs that fit rooms with different sizes and styles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eModern Fabric Sofas\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor minimalistic motifs, you can have one of Damro's modern fabric sofas. These include straight-lined sofas in colors that hold low-key designs. Such suits best homes that are already well-equipped with a modern feel to them.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLuxury Fabric Sofa Sets\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSophisticate the look of your living room with these luxurious fabric sofa sets. Featuring premium materials and exquisite detailing, these plush sofas also leave their mark in a bigger living space by adding sophistication to it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eGreat Customer Service\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro has earned its reputation not only for the superior quality of its products but also for its dedication to customer service. Right from the point of product inquiries to the delivery stage, the customer service team at Damro seeks to make the experience seamless and easy.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExpert Assistance:\u003c/strong\u003e If you cannot tell which in the range of fabric sofas would fit best in your home, these professionals can give suggestions on the appropriate style, sizing and even pricing of the sofa you wish to purchase.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAfter-Sales Support:\u003c/strong\u003e Damro, however, doesn’t stop providing services even after the sofa has been delivered to your doorstep. The consumer relations department is ready to address any issues regarding product maintenance, warranty, and repairs, even after the sale has been made.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro fabric sofas are the ideal choice for anyone seeking a combination of luxury sofas, modern design, and budget-friendly furniture. With their wide range of styles, premium materials, and competitive prices, Damro ensures that you’ll find the perfect fabric sofa to suit your needs. Their commitment to quality, sustainability, and exceptional customer service sets them apart in the world of home furniture.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhether you’re looking for a sleek, modern sofa in India, a budget-friendly option, or a luxury sofa to elevate your living room, Damro’s fabric sofas offer unmatched value. Explore their sofa sets online today and discover why Damro is the trusted choice for homeowners across India.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFAQs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e1. What types of fabric sofas does Damro offer?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro offers a variety of fabric sofas, including 3+2 sets, 3+1+1 sets, 3-seater sofas, and L-shaped fabric sofas. They cater to different room sizes and styles, from compact living rooms to large, open spaces.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e2. What fabrics are used in Damro fabric sofas?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro fabric sofas are available in several materials, including cotton blends, microfiber, linen, and velvet. Each fabric has its unique feel and durability, catering to various needs such as comfort, stain resistance, and luxurious looks.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3. What is the price range for Damro fabric sofas?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro fabric sofas typically range from ₹18,000 for basic models to over ₹107,000 for luxury designs. Prices vary based on the sofa's size, design, and fabric type.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e4. Are Damro fabric sofas durable?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYes, Damro fabric sofas are known for their durability. The frames are typically made from hardwood or metal, while the fabric is selected for its resistance to wear and tear. Fabrics like microfiber and linen are particularly durable for daily use.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e5. How do I maintain and clean a fabric sofa from Damro?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor everyday cleaning, vacuum the sofa regularly to remove dust and dirt. For stains, use a mild detergent and water solution to gently clean the fabric. Ensure you follow the specific cleaning instructions for the fabric type.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMicrofiber and linen are generally easier to clean, while velvet may require more delicate care.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e6. How do I choose the right size fabric sofa for my living room?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMeasure your living room before purchasing. For smaller rooms, a 3-seater or 3+1+1 set is ideal, while larger spaces can accommodate L-shaped sofas or 3+2 configurations. Make sure to leave enough room for movement around the sofa.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e7. Are there more options available for Damro fabric sofas?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYes, Damro offers more options for some models. You can choose from different fabric types, colours, and patterns to match your home’s interior.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e8. Can I buy Damro fabric sofas online?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYes, Damro fabric sofas are available for purchase online through their official website and other e-commerce platforms. Delivery services are offered across India, and you can also check for available discounts and deals online.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e9. What designs are available in Damro’s fabric sofa collection?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro offers a range of designs, from classic and traditional styles to modern and contemporary options. Whether you want a sleek minimalist design or a plusher, luxurious sofa, Damro has a variety of choices.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e10. Does Damro offer any deals or discounts on fabric sofas?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYes, Damro frequently offers deals and seasonal discounts on their fabric sofas. These discounts are often available during festive sales or promotional events. It's a good idea to check their website or showroom for ongoing offers.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","metaDescription":"Discover stylish fabric sofa sets online. Choose the best fabric for sofa designs and enjoy modern comfort with high-quality living room furniture.","metaKeywords":"fabric sofas, fabric couch, 2 seater fabric sofa, 3 seater fabric sofa, fabric sectional, comfortable fabric sofa, Damro fabric sofas","metaTitle":"Buy best Fabric Sofas \u0026 Premium Sofa Fabric Online Upto 40% Off","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Fabric Sofas | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/fabric-sofas\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse stylish and comfortable fabric sofas at Damro. Choose from a variety of sizes, colors, and designs to match your living room decor.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eThe comfort and elegance of Damro’s fabric sofa\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e574635de3d76d9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e574670a53d76da","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e5746e4143d76db","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e5746094b3d76dc","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e5746371b3d76dd","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e57465d943d76de","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e57462aea3d76df","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e57460dc63d76e0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e57462b9a3d76e1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e574679503d76e2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e5746e8ef3d76e3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e5746fd6d3d76e4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e574672993d76e5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e574673853d76e6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95ca60e57460ca63d76e7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"64ff0a8eab640c3c6bf1ad3d","ourcollection":true,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Leather Sofas","description":"Upgrade your living space with Damro’s premium leather sofas. Crafted in genuine leather and available in 2‑ and 3‑seater variants, these sofas offer rich aesthetics, robust build quality, and comfortable support. Ideal for modern homes seeking an upscale look with lasting durability.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/leather sofa.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b5ddd3a4604b0430f2bbac","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/leather sofa.jpg","hoverIcon":"","slug":"leather-sofas","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":1,"metaTitle":"Buy Modern Leather Sofa Set – Shop Luxury Designs Upto 30% Off","metaDescription":"Shop leather sofas online with style and durability. Choose luxury leather sofa sets, pure leather sofas, or modern leather sofa sets for comfort.","metaKeywords":"leather sofas online, genuine leather sofa, 3 seater leather sofa, 2 seater leather sofa, luxury leather sofa, Damro leather sofas","createdAt":"2023-09-11T12:39:42.660Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-28T16:06:33.673Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eBuy leather sofa online at the best price\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eLeather has for years dominated the luxury space and Damro has captured the essence in their sofas. Having used leather to craft elegance to redefine the concept of relaxation for your living space. You now indulge in the centerpiece of your home with a Damro leather sofa set\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eto glorify sophistication at all levels.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLet’s have a look at why the allure of Damro’s leather sofas is unbeatable:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eImpeccable craftsmanship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe exquisite detailing for each leather sofa; Damro\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003espeaks volumes about the skilled artisans. The meticulous designs on the leather sofas showcase superior craftsmanship. Working on the framework and constructing it for longevity and sturdiness without compromising on the style is what Damro’s collection offers.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePremium leather selection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe handpicked genuine leather promises unmatched elegance and comfort. Owning the opulence of leather sofas extends luxury to your home décor. Handpicked to adorn your homes with sophistication and opulence. You can buy spacious and grand leather sofas 3 seater or compact 2 seater for your homes. The leather is carefully sourced to become Damro’s premium sofas which improve with age.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfort redefined\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe soft and sleek surface of the leather sofas is unmatchable. While sinking into a plush leather sofa, you will feel the balance of softness and firmness intact. Leather sofas for living room\u0026nbsp;from Damro enable you to rejuvenate after a long day offering the best support and relaxation.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTimeless design\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLeather sofas symbolise classic décor, now with Damro’s touch of modern aesthetics, it can redefine your living space. Shopping for the best leather sofas online from Damro can save time and money. The sophisticated styles embrace the timeless beauty of leather and effortlessly add a touch of refinement to your homes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVersatility and durability\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDesigns and construction of leather sofas boast of luxury and comfort. The robust framework and high materials make the sofa resilient to constant usage. Damro sofa review shows satisfied customers while you enjoy yours. These sofas are built to last, ensuring years of comfort and enjoyment.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy maintenance\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s leather sofas may seem posh, yet they are easy to maintain and come under the easy-to-care-for category. When you check the sofa price,\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003ethe unbelievable offers for 2 or 3-seater leather sofas are unmatchable. To retain the pristine condition of your leather sofa at all times, wiping it with a soft and damp cloth can clear away any dust or spill.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePersonalized comfort\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePreferences of styles and designs can ensure your desired Damro leather sofa configurations. Depending on the layout of living spaces and requirements, create spacious or compact sofa designs to make your evenings special with friends and family or just you. You could make any choice for your home when you learn about Damro furniture prices.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTakeaway\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s leather sofa collection makes for a satisfying sofa-buying journey, as you can pick and customize elegant sofa sets that suit your needs. Whether you want leather sofas for office\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eor home, you will find them in our store. With impeccable quality and an affordable pricing range that exceeds your expectations in every way. Buying a leather sofa from Damro will elevate your home décor and be the perfect addition to your living space.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Leather Sofas | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/leather-sofas\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s range of premium leather sofas crafted with genuine leather and elegant design. Perfect for modern living spaces with long-lasting comfort.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover Damro’s Exquisite Leather Sofas\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d093931554c3c062bb6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d0939315573e9062bb7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d09393155b35f062bb8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d09393155870e062bb9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d093931559a2c062bba","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d093931551aba062bbb","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d0939315500da062bbc","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d093931557b16062bbd","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d093931550356062bbe","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d09393155c528062bbf","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d093931557d8c062bc0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d09393155606b062bc1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d093931556e6f062bc2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d09393155c577062bc3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d093931555fef062bc4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"60b5e00da4604b0430f2bbaf","name":"Corner Sofas","description":"Transform your living space with Damro’s stylish and functional corner sofas. Available in sleek L‑shaped and modular sectional styles, these sofas offer ample seating, premium upholstery, and smart layouts to fit any room. Ideal for families and guests, they combine comfort, durability, and contemporary design.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b5ddd3a4604b0430f2bbac","ourcollection":true,"icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","categoryImage":"","sortValue":2,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-28T16:07:32.718Z","__v":0,"slug":"corner-sofas","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eBuy your favorite corner sofa online from Damro\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eHomeowners in cities and urban areas opt for seating arrangements that don’t consume space. Corner sofas fit the bill with the right design to make your living room stylish yet don’t feel imposing on a room setting. When looking for elegance and appeal, corner sofas beat other furnishings by a large margin. Damro’s corner sofas for the living room symbolize modern comfort and functionality while catering to aesthetic appeal.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpace-saving designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro corner sofa set\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003edesigns are ingeniously crafted to optimize space for any space at home or office. They perfectly fit in apartments, small offices, and lobby area. Every inch of space is maximized without compromising on the comfort and style quotient. Corner sofas ensure enough legroom place for your other favourite décor in the house.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVersatile configurations\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFinding a corner sofa frame design that snugly fits your living space can get exhausting, however, Damro’s corner sofas convert every home décor better than before. Buyers can check out several configurations and preferences including left and right orientation.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eContemporary elegance\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe new corner sofa Damro\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003erequirements are diverse and multifunctional. Damro caters to modern aesthetics and works along with contemporary requirements in terms of trends, designs and outlook. Thus, allowing the buyer to look forward to clean lines, minimalistic design and premium upholstery. Your corner sofa can now effortlessly be the focal point of your décor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfortable seating experience\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s plush corner recliner sofas allow you to sink into the softly padded cushioning giving you the ultimate seating experience. The ergonomically designed corner sofas provide ample support and comfort when you sit back and relax. You will enjoy the same comfort and support each time you sit to lounge, get entertained or unwind\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable construction\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eRobust construction and sturdy frameworks crafted by trained artisans can withstand the rigours of regular use. High-quality upholstery ensures low maintenance and lesser chances to wear out. Damro’s corner leather sofas\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eare engineered for longevity ensuring you enjoy sitting on our sofas for many years.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFunctional features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur corner fabric sofas are high-functioning seats wherein you can enjoy the perfect seating experience also the ergonomic back support. The compactness of the design allows you to save space to move around easily. Easy to clean and maintain. Lesser wear and tear allowing to save costs. Additional features for your sofas such as recliners and storage compartments can customized as per requirement.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Personalized style\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSmaller and medium-sized homes have space constraints, while living space layouts in urban areas may require specific-designed sofas to fit into the room arrangement. We make sofas to reflect your individual taste and personality while complementing your existing décor. Damro caters to customizing corner sofas for sale just for you. Choose from a variety of fabrics, colours and finishes to create the perfect corner sofa for your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTakeaway\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSofas in every home become the centerpiece of the living room, buying a corner sofa makes that space, special. Damro’s production process contributes to impeccable styling and design. Buying our corner sofas online ensures you will join the league of satisfied customers who have experienced comfort and style.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","metaDescription":"Buy corner sofas that bring both comfort and style. Choose a corner sofa set or living room corner sofa made with sturdy build and lasting design.","metaKeywords":"corner sofas, L‑shaped sofas, sectional sofas, modular sofas, living room corner sofa, Damro corner sofas","metaTitle":"Buy Corner Sofas Online – Stylish Corner Sofa Sets Upto 40% Off","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Corner Sofas – L-Shaped \u0026 Sectional Sofas | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/corner-sofas\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s stylish and functional corner sofas. Discover L-shaped and sectional designs that fit perfectly into your living room while offering superior comfort and space efficiency.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDamro’s corner sofas for stylish comfort\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d443931553fcc062bc6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/bangalore-corner-sofas.jpg","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d443931556774062bc7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Raipur (3).jpg","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d4439315533c7062bc8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/chennai1.jpg","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d443931552b07062bc9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blo