damroimages/Kolkata (3).jpg","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d443931559f3e062bcf","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Kolkata (3).jpg","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d4439315545bd062bd0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/chennai1.jpg","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d443931557d98062bd1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/bangalore-corner-sofas.jpg","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d443931557752062bd2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/APTS (3).jpg","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d443931553564062bd3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Kolkata (3).jpg","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d443931557731062bd4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/3.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/corner sofas.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Raipur.jpg","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f","offer":""}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"60b5e023a4604b0430f2bbb0","name":"Wooden Sofas","description":"Explore Damro’s versatile range of wardrobes, featuring sliding and swing-door designs in 2‑, 3‑, and 4‑door options. Find the perfect match for your bedroom storage needs.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/4.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b5ddd3a4604b0430f2bbac","ourcollection":true,"icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/wooden sofas.jpg","categoryImage":"","sortValue":3,"trending":true,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-28T16:08:51.793Z","__v":0,"slug":"wooden-sofas","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eBuy your favorite wooden sofa at an affordable price\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eSofas made of wood exude classic charm and continue to be the first choice of sofa buyers. Damro’s wooden sofa set embodies the timeless elegance of the texture of wood and detailing. Wooden sofas are crafted with ample seating space to offer superb comfort. \u0026nbsp;The warmth and the feel of wood are incomparable to any other material while adding sophistication to any living space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExquisite craftsmanship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSkilled artisans work on every detail to create an enduring beauty. The quality of wood used and unparalleled artistry bring to life unmatched allure to Damro’s wooden sofa design. The superior construction and framework showcase the precision to adorn your living space. Damro’s high-quality finishing and ergonomic designs for wooden sofa sets are found in compact and spacious sofa selections.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNatural beauty of the wood\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe natural textures and rich grain patterns reflect the exquisite character of the premium material. Damro’s wooden sofa frame design is carefully made with wood showcasing charm and setting the ambiance of your home. The warm tones on the wooden sofa are inviting and relaxing, making a great space to unwind for the day.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTimeless design\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor ages, classic home furniture was crafted with wood. With time, Damro’s modern interpretation of using wood with classic silhouettes is catering to every taste and preference. Browsing through various options of wooden sofas,\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eDamro’s wooden sofa designs enable you to check how they have embraced timeless sophistication by adapting a diverse range of styles.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurability and longevity\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s sofas are made with carefully chosen hardwood for their beauty and structural integrity. The handpicked raw materials ensure durability and longevity to the entire framework even with regular usage. Despite the affordable sofa price,\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eour construction and structural integrity are retained due to impeccable craftsmanship.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfortable seating experience\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuying Damro’s wooden sofa is more than a piece of furniture it’s the seating experience that users relish. The plush padded cushioning and ergonomic designs ensure optimal relaxation and support. The sturdy framework and wooden sofa cushion offer support even when you lounge for hours on end.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVersatility in styling\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWooden sofa\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003estyled with modern aesthetics to meet the recent trends enabling you to integrate with the décor scheme is part of Damro’s collection. These sofas can adorn homes and commercial establishments with ample seating options. The effortless versatility of wooden sofas complements various interior styles with ease, providing buyers with endless options.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore options\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eChoose from any seating arrangement, from a 2 seater to a wooden sofa set 3+1+1in an affordable pricing range.\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eThe pick of upholstery, design and finish reflecting your style is perfectly crafted and delivered to you to complement your living space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTakeaway\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWooden sofas elevate home decor and Damro has mastered the craft of ensuring unmatched customer satisfaction. Whether it is committing to sustainable practices to wooden sofas online, we strive to exceed your expectations and provide you with a seamless shopping experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","metaDescription":"Upgrade your home with a premium wooden sofa set. Browse timeless wooden sofa designs, practical sofa cum bed wooden, and stylish modern wooden sofas.","metaKeywords":"Wooden sofa sets","metaTitle":"Buy Premium Wooden Sofas \u0026 Sofa Cum Bed Wooden – Save Upto 35% Today","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Wardrobes – Sliding \u0026 Swing-Door Options | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/wardrobes\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s collection of wardrobes online. Featuring durable and stylish sliding and swing-door designs in 2-, 3-, and 4-door configurations.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover the elegance of Damro’s wooden sofas\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e57464d8f3d76e9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e574619203d76ea","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e57466af13d76eb","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e574628e73d76ec","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e5746c91c3d76ed","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e5746145e3d76ee","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e574636e23d76ef","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e574648953d76f0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e574611663d76f1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e574610103d76f2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e574653fc3d76f3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e5746ec363d76f4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e5746388c3d76f5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e57464d623d76f6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95d930e5746c4be3d76f7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"64f1b217ab640cab71f15b98","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Sofa Sets","description":"Explore our diverse range of Sofa Sets tailored to fit any interior setting. Whether you seek modern sophistication or classic charm, our collection caters to various styles. Embrace the opportunity to revitalize your living room with furniture that seamlessly blends into your aesthetic, offering both comfort and a touch of elegance.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/5.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b5ddd3a4604b0430f2bbac","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/sofa sets.jpg","hoverIcon":"","slug":"sofa-sets","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":4,"metaTitle":"Buy Sofa Set for Hall Online – Modern Designs Up to 35% Off","metaDescription":"Shop sofa sets online that combine comfort and design. From modern sofa set designs to versatile sofa sets for hall, find the right fit for your space.","metaKeywords":"Living room sofa sets, Sectional sofas and couches, Two-seater and three-seater sofas, Upholstered sofa collections, Modern and classic sofa designs","createdAt":"2023-09-01T09:42:47.542Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-28T16:09:39.214Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eFind Stylish Sofa Set Online at Best Prices\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn search of an Elegant, Affordable, and comfy sofa in India? Damro is on top of things! Recognised for its outstanding selection of contemporary and traditional styles, Damro provides couches that blend in with any decor and are made with high-quality materials for long-lasting comfort. DAMRO is the trusted name for consumers nationwide, when it comes to affordable and stylish sofa sets. whether they are updating their living area, outfitting a new house, or searching for a sofa set.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eWhat to search for while selecting sofa set and loungers?\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eLength\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMaterial\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eComfort\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eSelecting your sofa size\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen selecting the scale of your couch, there are vital things to take into account. Firstly, the sofa ought should be spacious enough to comfortably accommodate your family members. Secondly, it has to no longer be too massive or too small for the room in which it will likely be placed. At Damro, you can find sofa set styles in a variety of sizes, all at Affordable prices. Some of the not-unusual sizes to be had consist of:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e1 Seater sofa set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/single-seaters\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003esingle-seater sofa \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003etakes up minimal space and may be placed anywhere around the house, including the bedroom, residing room, study room, and many others. you may even choose a 1 seater recliner sofa and region it near your examination desk to create an inviting and analyzing nook.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e2 Seater sofa set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/two-seaters-sofas\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTwo-seater sofas\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e are huge sufficient to seat 2 humans and compact sufficient to be located in any small area, which includes your Living room, bedroom, office, and so on.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3 Seater sofa set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eGiven that these sofas can accommodate three people, \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/three-seaters-sofas\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3-seater sofas \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003eare best for any medium-sized drawing room or living room.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e4 Seater sofa Set\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA 4 seater sofa set can be a great desire for a big residing room. You can opt for LHS and RHS sectional sofas to create a fashion statement and set off the decor with a complementing coffee desk.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e5 Seater sofa Set\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe five-seater sofa sets are splendid for massive families to spend time together. They offer you with the alternatives of 3+2, 3+1+1, and a pair of 2+1 mixtures and shaped sofa units. You may set up them depending on your preference.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e6 Seater sofa set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn case you love having buddies and family over for get-togethers, having a spacious 6-seater can be a perfect desire. Choosing a breakdown aggregate of 3+2+1 will assist you to create a spacious and sophisticated look.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e7 Seater Sofas Set\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWant to look at fits at home on the TV with a big group of pals? A 7-seater sofa in a 3+2+2 combination at Damro can provide ample space for at-ease seating and lend your huge residing room a classy appearance.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eThe way to choose your sofa set material?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003ePerfect fabric selection is important since it affects not only comfort but how easy it would be to maintain and how long it would last.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric:\u003c/strong\u003e Fabric sofas come with softness, with an option of colours and patterns. They fit when you want to lounge. They are good for homes with little kids since they offer warmth. While Damro's fabric sofas offer plush comfort, make sure the durability and resistance to stains in the selected fabric are solid.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLeather:\u003c/strong\u003e Leather is cool, smokeless, and non-greasy hence suitable for a more classy look. It's also not easy on the pocket and thus not ideal for houses with pets or kids as they might scratch them.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMicrofiber\u003c/strong\u003e: Microfiber is another very resistant synthetic material, and it looks like suede. They are the best for consumers who desire abrasion resistance but do not want to lose comfort.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVelvet:\u003c/strong\u003e Velvet sofas are the epitome of luxury; thus they are perfect for making the room feel rich, though they might demand some more careful maintenance.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eA way to pick out a relaxed sofa set model?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhilst it's a question of consolation, not all sofas are constructed equal. You will locate the most relaxed wood sofa units right here at affordable price at Damro. Preserve these things in mind whilst deciding on your wood sofa set online:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSeat intensity:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eYour sofa depth can decide how at ease you may feel whilst sitting on it. Choose a deeper seat if you are tall and a shallower seat if your peak is short.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBack height:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eA higher back seat will make you more comfortable if you have a tall peak. For shorter people, a sofa with a preferred returned top may be suitable.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSofa Arm fashion:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eDepending on how you spend time on a sofa, you may pick the sofa arm style. As instance, if you prefer to rest your head on wooden sofa palms, a settee with padded and rounded fingers could be an extremely good preference. In any other case, you can go for a sofa with glossy, thin arms.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCushion Filling:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eDo you decide upon sinking into a settee proper away or want the cushion to conform to your frame slowly when you sit on it? Based on your choice, you can move for high-density foam filling, down stuffing as your sofa cushion filling.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eHow a Designer Sofa Can Elevate Your Room\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eA well-chosen designer sofa can be the focal point of your living room, enhancing both the aesthetics and functionality of the space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMatching the Design:\u003c/strong\u003e If your room has a minimalist look, go for a simple designs. For a more luxurious space, choose a plush, bold-coloured sofa with intricate designs. Damro’s collection offers both contemporary and classic styles, making it easy to find a match.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore Options:\u003c/strong\u003e Many designer sofas offer a variety of fabric and leather color options, allowing you to choose the perfect combination to suit your taste and complement your room’s decor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eContrast:\u003c/strong\u003e A sofa set with a striking contrast to the room's colour palette can make a dramatic statement. For instance, a vibrant-coloured sofa in a neutral-toned room can add vibrancy and personality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eDamro: Your ultimate destination for designer sofa sets\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe at Damro provide sofas and furniture portions which are excessive in great, consolation, and style. Whatever your decor style, you can locate your ideal sofa match at our online keep. Our range of sofa units is supposed to be rather durable and are available in various charge degrees. On pinnacle of that, we offer superb reductions. This makes our sofa set pricing even more attractive. If you're looking for an impressive sofa set at a low fee, Damro offers the best alternatives at an affordable price.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePeople preference - Trending sofa design\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSofasets have evolved from useful furnishings to elegant centrepieces that set the tone for your living room decor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAngular Sofas:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eAngular sofas like L-fashioned designs have emerged as a famous fashion thanks to their unconventional silhouette that lends itself superbly to trendy rooms. Those angular sofas seamlessly fit into corners or wrap-round walls, adding ample seating whilst wrapping your decor in a cutting-edge style. Whilst considering an angular sofa for your house, it’s critical to compare the sofa set charge in India to make certain you're getting the best fee on your investment.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMinimalist Sofas:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eMinimalist sofas embody the less-is-extra layout precept with easy forms, smooth and crisp strains, and a neutral, pared-again palette. They epitomise understated beauty with a stability between capability and aesthetic simplicity. those stay distinctly sought-after as they lend even the smallest living rooms an increased, breezy appearance. Given the growing trend, the sofa set fee in India for minimalist designs can range, with alternatives to be had for both price range-aware consumers and those searching out top class portions.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAntique fashion Sofas:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAntique-stimulated sofas showcase hallmarks of the ornate patterns frequent in bygone eras. Carved timber frames, generously rolled palms, and lush luxe fabrics like velvet lend them their uniquely spellbinding aura. Their undying attraction provides an on-the-spot dose of luxury and gravitas to interiors with their air of secrecy of antique-international elegance.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMultifunctional sofa Beds:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eMultifunctional sofa set alternatives provide smart convertible seating answers geared to space-strapped modern homes. They permit rooms to integrate twin-purpose visitor bed capability. Their flexible multi-use format fits the fluid lifestyles of present-day city dwellers, wherein in a single day guests are an everyday feature. Relying on the attributes, the sofa set fee in India for those multifunctional designs can vary broadly, providing picks that fit numerous budgetary wishes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eShop sofa sets online according to the price variety at Damro\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eMost of the time, it so occurs that the chosen sofa set layout may barely fall out of finances. Then sadly, you need to give up and begin your seek all over again. With Damro, you may at once start your seek by way of deciding on your sofa set fee range, thanks to the rate filter out.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can pick from the subsequent furniture sofa set charge variety:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSofa sets under Rs. 30,000: Buy a settee set from this elegant collection to enhance your luxurious decor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSofa units beneath Rs. 40,000: You will discover a lavish collection of sofa sets under this price range.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSofa sets underneath Rs. 50,000: A premium variety of sofa units online will remodel the aesthetics of your room.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSofa sets above Rs. 50,000: Redefine luxury and comfort with those premium sofa units and create an ideal decor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eAn Abundance of Styles for Everyone\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro has always taken pride in being able to design a range of sets that will suit many tastes and preferences all over the country. Are you looking for modern, minimalistic, or any more formal principles? Look no further, Damro has all that and many more. The extensive range of styles enables every customer to choose the most appropriate sofa for the style of the house or a design in any of the rooms that will act as the centre of attraction.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eModern Designs\u003c/strong\u003e: Every admirer of stylish and contemporary furniture cannot ignore the modern and luxury sofas designed by Damro. The sofas come in perfect straight lines, natural shades and futuristic shapes-fashion at its best. Such designs are ideal for city houses or flats since emphasis is placed on utility, and elegance is not sacrificed.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eClassic Designs:\u003c/strong\u003e For those who cherish enduring elegance, the charm of classic sofas with subtle restraint is still within reach. Such designs feature plush seating, wooden accents, and luxurious fabrics that enhance the aesthetic of any lounge.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSectional Sofas:\u003c/strong\u003e Damro has sectional sofas for bigger rooms or families who need extra spaces to sit on. These sofas provide diversity in the arrangement and positioning of seats enabling you to use up the space and be able to create a nice seating area that is comfortable and looks together.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSofas for Small Spaces:\u003c/strong\u003e Damro has shown consideration to small houses or apartments by also providing small sofas manufactured with such houses in mind. These are stylish functional sofas, which if fitted in a corner do not physically crowd the space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuality Materials for Quality Seating Over Extensive Usage\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe major benefit of Damro's sofa set range is derived from the perfect quality of the materials. Durability has always been a key consideration when it comes to buying furniture, and so Damro uses the best fabrics, wood, and foams to craft its sofas which are more durable over time.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFabric Sofa Set options\u003c/strong\u003e: Damro has a variety of sofas with all types of sofa set coverings ranging from soft and fluffy fabric to even leatherette that is easy to clean. Whether it is a fabric or leather these Damro sofas will please all the clients in those particular fields.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable Frames:\u003c/strong\u003e The Strong and Sturdy frame is the foundation of exceptional comfort, and Damro excels in maintaining that quality. Their sofa sets are made of hard timbers such as solid wood and engineered wood, which ensures your investment is well-built and as well as secure.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHigh-Quality Foam:\u003c/strong\u003e Of course, this is very important, and this is the reason why Damro's sofas have high, dense foam that gives comfortable cushions. So be it a swift coffee break or a lazy extended binge-watching session, your Sofas will strike the right cord of firmness and comfort because of its High Density foam structure.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCost-Effectiveness without Quality Loss\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe most interesting unique selling proposition (USP) of Damro, lies in its provision of high-quality sofas at reasonable prices. Damro, on the other hand, manages to achieve a perfect blending of low prices with high-quality levels of the products.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro designs its sofa sets to suit all pockets and thus has a large customer market base. Whether you are a first-time young professional looking to furnish an apartment, or a family simply refurbishing their living room, there is a Damro sofa within your reach that will suit your purposes and most importantly your purse.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLow-Cost Options\u003c/strong\u003e: Damro does not compromise on quality and design in its cheap furniture range. For even the cheap sofa sets, the same effort and quality of materials used in midlevel and high-end prices are used so that a customer gets value for their money.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMid-Range and Luxury Options:\u003c/strong\u003e For those who might want something more exquisite, Damro does stock high-end sofas, with high-quality leather, complex designs and extra comfort features. These options offer a better look and comfort that is difficult to find elsewhere at such reasonable prices.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBuy Sofa Sets Online: Convenience and Flexibility:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn today’s fast-paced world, convenience is key. Damro recognizes this and offers the option to buy sofa sets online. This allows customers to browse their extensive catalogues from the comfort of their homes, compare designs, and read reviews before making a purchase. Their user-friendly website makes it easy to select the perfect sofa, place an order, and have it delivered to your doorstep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOnline Shopping:\u003c/strong\u003e With a well-organized online store, Damro allows you to explore their full range of sofa sets, complete with detailed descriptions, specifications, and images. This makes it easier for customers to make informed decisions without having to visit a physical store.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDelivery and Installation:\u003c/strong\u003e Once you’ve made your purchase, Damro takes care of the rest. Their delivery service ensures your sofa arrives in perfect condition, and their team handles the installation, so you don’t have to worry about setting it up yourself.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAchieving 100% Customer Satisfaction\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe best products rendered useless in terms of service are not good enough, and Damro pays great attention to this part. For instance, if you bought a sofa set from Damro, their customer service can assist you from the moment of the inquiry to the time of delivery. Be it product selection or simply after-sales support, their team strives to make the experience seamless and enjoyable.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eWhat Makes Damro Your Ultimate Sofa Solution?\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen it comes to buying sofas in India, Damro is one of the best options due to its Affordable prices, use of high-quality fabrics and availability of different kinds of designs. Be it a luxury sofa set, modern design or even Budget-Friendly Sofas, Damro has it all so you are assured of getting something for your house. Also, with the facilities of online shopping, Store Collection, and customer care centres, Buying a sofa from Damro is one of the most enjoyable experiences you can have.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSo, if you want to get a new sofa set that combines style, functionality and Value for money all together, thanks to Damro!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFAQs:\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e1. What types of sofa sets does Damro offer?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro offers a wide range of sofa sets, including fabric, leather, and wooden sofas. Their collections range from traditional to contemporary designs, including sectional sofas, recliners, and classic two- and three-seaters.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e2. What is the price range of Damro sofa sets?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe price of Damro sofa sets varies based on the material, size, and design. You can find budget-friendly options starting from ₹28,000 to more premium designs that go upwards of ₹1,00,000.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3. What materials are available for Damro sofa sets?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro sofa sets come in various materials, including fabric, leather, faux leather, microfiber, and velvet. Wooden frame sofas are also available for a more traditional look.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e4. How do I choose the right size of a sofa for my living room?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo choose the right size, measure the dimensions of your living room and the space where the sofa will be placed. Damro offers sofas in various sizes, from compact two-seaters for smaller spaces to larger sectional sofas for bigger living rooms.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e5. Do Damro sofa sets have more collection's?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYes, Damro offers more options on certain models. You can choose different fabrics, colors, and cushion types to fit your personal style and the décor of your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e6. How durable are Damro sofa sets?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro sofas are known for their durability. The frames are typically made from Solid wood, and the upholstery materials are designed to withstand regular use. Leather and microfiber models tend to offer extra longevity.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e7. How do I maintain and clean a Damro sofa?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor fabric sofas, vacuum regularly and clean stains with mild soap and water. Leather sofas can be wiped with a damp cloth and conditioned with leather cleaner to maintain softness. Always follow the manufacturer’s care instructions for the specific material.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e8. Do Damro sofas come with a warranty?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYes, Damro sofa sets come with a warranty, typically ranging from 1 to 3 years depending on the model and type. The warranty generally covers manufacturing defects but may not cover wear and tear.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e9. Can I buy a Damro sofa set online?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYes, Damro offers online purchasing options through its official website and other e-commerce platforms. You can browse their collections, check reviews, and place an order for home delivery.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e10. Does Damro offer delivery and installation services?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYes, Damro provides delivery and installation services. Most of their sofa sets come with free delivery within certain regions, and they also offer professional installation to ensure your sofa is set up properly.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebSite\",\n  \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/sofas\",\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"{search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eBest Sofa Set Online at Damro Stores Across India\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Category Page opt 2 - Sofa.jpg","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc33931556cd0062bd6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/5.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Category Page opt 2 - Sofa.jpg","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc3393155a550062bd7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc339315536c7062bd8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc33931555be1062bd9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc33931554131062bda","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc3393155b459062bdb","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc339315537c8062bdc","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc3393155caca062bdd","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc33931559b16062bde","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc3393155bd44062bdf","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc33931556594062be0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc3393155719c062be1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc33931552a2e062be2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc33931551c16062be3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95dc33931554cad062be4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"6291d8994d9f7fad0095ac9b","ourcollection":true,"trending":true,"enable":true,"name":"Sofa Beds","description":"Optimize your living area with Damro’s versatile Sofa Beds—combining the comfort of a sofa with the convenience of a bed. Perfect for compact homes and guest rooms, these pieces feature soft upholstery and smooth unfolding mechanisms. Style meets functionality in designs that elevate your space while adding practical value.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/6.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b5ddd3a4604b0430f2bbac","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/sofa beds.jpg","slug":"sofa-bed","sortValue":5,"metaTitle":"Buy sofa cum bed online and explore stylish sofa beds up to 40% off","metaDescription":"Find the right sofa bed for your space. Explore sofa bed sets, sturdy sofa cum bed wooden, and modern wooden sofa beds built for lasting use.","metaKeywords":"sofa bed, convertible sofa, sleeper sofa, space-saving furniture, guest sofa, Damro sofa bed","createdAt":"2022-05-28T08:08:57.940Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-28T16:10:30.806Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eShop affordable sofa cum bed\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe concept of sofa beds in urban areas has gained momentum with many furniture brands redesigning sofa sets for multifunctional uses. Damro’s collection of sofa cum beds has seamlessly adopted the sofa bed set concept for delivering a perfect solution to modern living spaces. Damro’s sofa beds have achieved a seamless transition of seating and sleeping features without compromising on style and comfort.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpace-saving design\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eCompact homes and smaller living room layouts need a sofa with stylish seating by the day and a comfortable bed by night. These sofa cum beds offer practical solutions for saving space in small to medium-sized houses. Sofa beds work well for apartment homes, guest rooms, or multipurpose spaces, being a cost-effective option while saving space.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDual functionality\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSofa beds for sale\u003c/strong\u003e from Damro easily convert from a plush sofa to a comfortable bed in no time. Versatile furniture pieces like sofa cum beds are trending with more customers opting for space-saving solutions. The changeover is of great convenience when you have guests overnight or sleepovers. Even when you want to lounge and binge-watch your favorite show, sofa cum beds make it the most relaxing way to do it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStylish designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMost multifunctional furnishings lack aesthetic appeal. However, Damro’s sofa beds\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eonline collection has the most stylish designs and finishes to take home. Customization of the designs with individual preferences and tastes is accommodated. We offer a variety of sofa beds including classic to modern designs, and sleek to pattern ones that suit every taste and preference.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Comfortable sleeping experience\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOften a misconception of sofa beds not being comfortable enough for the sleeper, Damro sofa bed price has broken that myth with plush cushioning and firm padding is also affordable. The smooth upholstery and sturdy framework allow a good night’s sleep. The ergonomic design and optimal support ensure you wake up refreshed.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurability and Longevity\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLong-lasting sofa beds\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003efrom Damro are crafted from high-density PU foam and premium tailored fabric to withstand regular usage. The sturdiness of the construction of the sofa bed delivers functionality for years to come providing you best comfort and convenience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy maintenance\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eLow-maintenance and cost-effective sofa cum bed is a big hit with customers. Removable covers and easy-to-clean materials ensure hassle-free upkeep. Less time and effort spent on cleaning means a lot of time to relax and enjoy your well-deserved free time lounging on your sofa bed.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpace-saving storage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOptimizing storage space with sofa cum beds because of a storage compartment will blow your mind away. The in-built storage feature is part of Damro’s sofa bed benefits\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eallowing you to store blankets and other accessories conveniently. This \u0026nbsp;is not only a multifunctional furnishing but also helps keep your space organized and clutter-free.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTakeaway\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTransform your living space with more functional furnishings, like the Damro sofa cum bed.\u0026nbsp;Now hosting overnight guests is no longer a problem with our space-saving sofa beds offering comfort and versatility to meet your needs. With affordable sofa beds in our collection, elevate your living space experience.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Sofa Beds – Stylish \u0026 Space‑Saving | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/sofa-bed\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s convertible sofa beds that effortlessly transform from sleek sofas to comfortable guest beds. Perfect for modern flats, guest rooms, and versatile living spaces.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eVersatile Living Options with Damro’s Sofa cum Beds\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95df6393155f57c062be6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95df6393155486c062be7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95df6393155a45a062be8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68d95df6393155aa87062be9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"