"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da222ba54b7f36d9c318ca","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da222ba54b7fe0e5c318cb","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da222ba54b7f2c86c318cc","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da222ba54b7f6499c318cd","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da222ba54b7f6a44c318ce","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"64f1b64fab640cbdd8f15b9f","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Recliner Sets","description":"Transform your living room into a cozy retreat with Damro’s Recliner Sets. Choose from 2‑seater or 3‑seater options in luxurious fabric or genuine leather, featuring both manual and electric reclining mechanisms for tailored comfort and a stylish upgrade to your home entertainment area.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/12.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b5e0a1a4604b0430f2bbb1","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"recliner-sets","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":3,"metaTitle":"Buy recliner sofa set online stylish comfort up to 30% off","metaDescription":"Discover stylish recliner sofa sets online. Explore cozy recliner seats and the best reclining sofas designed for relaxation and modern living.","metaKeywords":"recliner sets, fabric recliner sets, leather recliner sets, 2 seater recliner set, 3 seater recliner set, Damro recliners, living room recliners","createdAt":"2023-09-01T10:00:47.161Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:08:35.033Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eTransform any home décor or office space easily and offer comfort and style when you have recliner sets from Damro. Find a perfect solution of luxury and sophistication in a single furniture piece by bringing home recliner sets. Pick recliner set for hosting movie nights and family gatherings while providing spacious seating options. Damro’s collection has a full range of recliners also available in their online catalogue to choose from and enhance your living space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfort redefined\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eErgonomically designed recliner sets from Damro ensure you have the perfect lumber support while you sit or recline. The perfect headrest and padded armrests ensure the ultimate comfort. The changing reclining positions and plush seating provided a luxurious seating experience. With manual and electric options available to cater for your preferences and needs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStyle options for every home\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhether you prefer modern or classic décor for homes or blend of both can be personalised to suit your requirements. We have the perfect recliner living room sets that complement any living space. Those who love minimalistic can check out various recliner finishes and designs from Damro’s collection. Options of leather or fabric recliners enhance the aesthetic appeal of your home’s ambience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Durability and craftsmanship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePremium material and robust framework ensure your recliner sets last a long time even after daily usage. Sturdy recliners with quality craftsmanship showcase long-lasting durability in the Damro recliner sofa set collection. A variety of fabric and leather options in recliner sofa sets that stylishly can complement your existing furniture and décor. Carefully selected upholstery ensures no easy wear and tear with low maintenance required to retain the recliner set’s beauty and functionality for several years.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eRecliners come in single-seater chairs, two-seater sofas, three-seater sofa options and recliner sofa set 3+2 with Multiple features at Damro’s recliner sets collection. Additional features of adjustable headrests, built-in cup holders and storage compartments can be part of your recliner sets. Manual or electric recliner sets are available according to your comfort preferences. The innovative features in recliner sets not only provide a plush look but give out a luxurious feel which a normal chair or sofa may not provide.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eValue and affordability\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen you want to create a personalized living space with elegance, recliner sets can help in providing a luxurious appearance and superior quality within budget. Damro recliner sets can elevate any office or home décor with comfort and value. In terms of functionality and enjoyment recliner sets form an experience in itself. Damro recliner sofa\u0026nbsp;promises an assured product that comes with warranty and customer satisfaction making it the best buy in furnishings.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTakeaway\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eRecliners provide the perfect blend of comfort and functionality giving your cozy family room a makeover. Even your office space will get a makeover with a recliner set. Damro’s recliner chair\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eis a great addition for providing sophistication to your lounge area and also bringing home the theatre experience on movie nights. Since your recliner sets come from Damro, you can enjoy comfort and aesthetic appeal for many years to come.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Recliner Sets – Fabric \u0026 Leather Recliners | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/recliner-sets\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s recliner set collection including 2‑seater and 3‑seater options in fabric and leather. Designed for superior comfort and style in your living room.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfort and style with Damro’s recliner set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f510ec318d0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f4fe5c318d1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f042bc318d2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f4c89c318d3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f7130c318d4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f0c10c318d5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7fa055c318d6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7fd98bc318d7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f2d06c318d8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f02c1c318d9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7fd9c3c318da","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f2c65c318db","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f23a8c318dc","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f0688c318dd","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2263a54b7f887cc318de","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"60b5e15ca4604b0430f2bbb3","name":"Single Seater Recliners","description":"Create a restful sleep haven with Damro’s Single Mattresses. Choose from memory foam for pressure relief, coir for natural support, or traditional spring for bounce and resilience. Compact yet supportive, these mattresses are ideal for children’s rooms, guest beds, and smaller spaces—delivering comfort and quality night after night.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/13.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b5e0a1a4604b0430f2bbb1","ourcollection":true,"icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/single 6 seater.jpg","categoryImage":"","sortValue":4,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:10:24.242Z","__v":0,"slug":"single-seater-fabric-leather-recliners","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eDamro’s single seater\u0026nbsp;recliners\u0026nbsp;can transform any office space or living area into an elegant and stylish haven. Crafted individually to suit taste and preference while providing ultimate relaxation. Premium materials are\u0026nbsp;used\u0026nbsp;to provide the perfect blend of comfort and functionality. Purchase Damro’s single seater recliner\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003esofa under 20000\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eand enjoy all the great features it has to offer.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eKey Features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePremium features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eErgonomic design and plush cushioning provide the perfect seating experience. The sleek design and elegant finish add to the touch of sophistication that Damro’s single-seater recliners demonstrate. Upgrade your seating arrangement with our manual and\u0026nbsp;recliner sofa single seater\u0026nbsp;electric motor\u0026nbsp;versions of the recliners with additional features of cup holders and in-built charging ports and\u0026nbsp;host of\u0026nbsp;other features\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSmooth reclining mechanism\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eSeveral reclining positions right up to 180 degrees effortlessly through manual or electric mechanisms are available in recliner sofa single-seater Damro. The backrest provides full support when you recline backwards with an extended footrest. Extra padding allows you to relax when reclining in any position while lounging on your single-seater. The flexibility of customizing your positions helps you choose the ideal angle of relaxation with buttons on the sides.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable build\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe durable construction and sturdy recliner framework will ensure long-lasting appeal even after regular usage. Damro’s recliner sofa single-seater leather uses premium upholstery while the entire furniture piece has a warranty assuring the customer of a quality product. The control on the recliners works smoothly and provides gradual movement to the ideal position you choose to rest in without jerky movements.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCompact design\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eRecliners that fit in compact spaces or get personalized dimensions at Damro’s recliner collection. Despite the take on size, maximum style and comfort are maintained without any compromise. Buying a quality recliner that doesn’t consume much space yet provides a relaxing experience each time you sit back to unwind for the day. Compact recliners from Damro also provide adequate lumber support while diligence on elegance and style are equally proportional. Optimized functionality and affordability of the single recliner sofa price\u0026nbsp;are offered to the customer.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith several years of experience in delivering furniture and crafting premium pieces that adorn millions of Indian Homes, Damro has elevated lifestyle with its furniture range. We have worked on comfort durability and style to exceed expectations. Our goal lies beyond the quality craftsmanship of single seater recliners. We pride ourselves on the utmost customer satisfaction and the meticulous design of these luxury seaters. With low maintenance requirements and warranty assured, Damro ticks every box.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExplore our collection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSingle-seater recliners in every colour and design to complement every home décor. From classic to contemporary aesthetics Damro’s single-seater recliner range offer to complements your personal style and taste.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTransform your home today\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eGet the latest collection of single-seater recliners. Purchasing a recliner will not just upgrade your décor but help unwind the day in luxury.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrder yours today\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYour spaces can be converted into a blend of elegance and comfort with our range of furniture solutions.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eContact us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eElevate your homes today with single-seater recliners from Damro Today!\u003c/p\u003e","metaDescription":"Relax in style with a recliner sofa single seater. Browse the best single seater recliners and shop single seater recliner sofas online for cozy seating.","metaKeywords":"single mattress, memory foam single mattress, coir mattress single, spring mattress single, kids mattress, Damro mattresses","metaTitle":"Buy Recliner Sofa Single Seaters Online with Premium Comfort","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Single-Seater Fabric \u0026 Leather Recliners | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/single-seater-fabric-leather-recliners\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s collection of single-seater fabric and leather recliners, offering both comfort and contemporary design. Ideal for living rooms and home theater setups.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eExplore the comfort and Style of Damro’s single seater recliner\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Recliner.jpg","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7f906ec318e0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/1 Recliners.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/1 Sliding Banners  - Recliner.jpg","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7f20e5c318e1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7fbf5cc318e2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7f4385c318e3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7fbdb7c318e4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7f57b4c318e5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7f1e05c318e6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7f1615c318e7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7fb959c318e8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da22d0a54b7fcaf4c318e9","categoryspaceimage