query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e","sortValue":3,"description":"Curate your ideal bedroom with Damro’s thoughtfully designed furniture collection. From beds and wardrobes to bedside tables and dressers, our products combine elegance, practicality, and durability—helping you craft a cozy, coordinated, and functional sleeping space.\n\n","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/5 Bed.jpg","subcategory":[{"_id":"60b61326a4604b0430f2bbca","name":"Beds","slug":"beds","image":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/21.jpg","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/5 Bed.jpg","description":"Transform your bedroom with Damro’s versatile bed collection. Choose from sturdy wooden frames and space-efficient storage models to luxurious upholstered designs. Engineered for comfort, style, and longevity—our beds are tailor-made to match your space and lifestyle.\n\n","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Beds – Wooden, Storage \u0026 Upholstered Beds | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/beds\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop beds online from Damro including storage beds, wooden beds, hydraulic beds, and upholstered designs. Perfect for stylish and functional bedrooms.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"649528d177c6ad70b8af2961","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Queen Beds without Storage","description":"Elevate your bedroom with Damro’s Queen Beds Without Storage. Combining timeless design and robust construction, these beds feature quality wooden or upholstered frames without built-in storage—ideal for a minimalist and elegant bedroom aesthetic.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/19.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61326a4604b0430f2bbca","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"queen-beds-without-storage","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":0,"metaTitle":"Buy Queen Size Beds Without Storage Online with upto 35% off","metaDescription":"Upgrade your bedroom with a queen size bed without storage. Explore queen size wooden beds without storage and shop premium queen beds online.","metaKeywords":"queen beds without storage, queen size bed, wooden queen bed, upholstered queen bed, minimalist bed, Damro beds","createdAt":"2023-06-23T05:08:33.328Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:14:57.919Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eFurnishing homes has never been easy, especially finding a high-quality and stylish \u003cstrong\u003equeen size bed without storage\u003c/strong\u003e for the bedroom. Look no further, as Damro has a diverse selection and affordable pricing options in its range of queen size beds. These queen size beds meet both aesthetic and functional requirements. Whether you prefer a minimalistic or space-saving solution, Damro collection has some popular models that cater to every customer need.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eOur top-rated Queen Beds Without Storage\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eZaira queen-size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eA perfect queen-size bed that is simple and compact makes a great fit for smaller bedrooms. Modern homes can do well with sturdy construction and functionality with Damro’s \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/lscwbza003-bed-zaira-queen-size-bd220115-mild-natural-8684-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eZaira\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003esolid wood queen-size bed without storage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e. Expert craftsmen work on exquisite design and detailing while adding elegance to the queen-size bed. The bed checks all the boxes of durability and warranty of 12 months for its long-lasting design.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHeritage queen-size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eOwning a \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/lscwbhe003-bed-heritage-queen-size-bd211235-rose-wood-8689-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHeritage queen-sized bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e can become a versatile addition to your bedroom. The sleek and minimalistic design has aesthetic value enhancing your bedroom décor. The queen size bed comes with a lacquered finish and brass studs. The sturdy construction with Sheesham wood queen size bed without storage\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eforms the base structure providing durability.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBrilliant queen-bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/nbbr003-natural-veneer-bed-brilliant-teak-2814-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAn affordably priced queen-sized bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e that could adorn your bedroom. Damro's queen-size bed dimensions match modern homes while having a sleek and compact design without storage. The high headboard provides good back support while watching TV or reading. The use of solid wood and lacquered finish gives a modern touch to the high-quality long-lasting design.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrnate queen-size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuying a queen-size bed with sturdy construction and sophistication from Damro’s collection can be a great addition to your home. \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kbo003-kd-bed-ornate-wgm42-9186-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOrnate queen-sized bed design without storage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e with ample space for sleep because of the generous dimensions add a touch of elegance to your bedroom. The ornate detailing and style catch match your décor preferences.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro is known for locally sourced and sustainable manufacturing. Using excellent craftsmanship for each furniture piece and selling at affordable rates, a Damro queen size bed price makes it a popular choice. These specifically designed beds with no storage match various interiors seamlessly providing both functionality and comfort. Here are more reasons why Damro can match your needs:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePremium materials\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eSolid wood and high-quality detailing accessories and finishing ensure durability and longevity.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Affordable pricing\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eGet a premium quality Damro bed queen size at affordable pricing matching your budget and preference.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Wide range\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eA variety of finishes, designs, dimensions\u0026nbsp; and customized options are part of our collection\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Customer support\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur excellent customer support helps you pick the best queen-size bed matching your preferences and décor.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eElevate every bedroom with Damro’s queen-size bed collection. We provide high-quality products and innovative designs to transform your space into a haven for relaxation. Check out our latest range and take advantage of our ongoing discounts on \u003cstrong\u003equeen size bed without storage online\u003c/strong\u003e. Buy one today and experience the quality and comfort firsthand!\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Queen Size Beds Without Storage | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/queen-beds-without-storage\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop queen size beds without storage at Damro. Crafted with premium materials and elegant designs, these beds offer comfort and timeless appeal.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover Queen Beds Without Storage From Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f338fc31910","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f9063c31911","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7fea84c31912","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f2a43c31913","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7fb34fc31914","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f08ddc31915","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7fdd2fc31916","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f3fc7c31917","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f6121c31918","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f44f3c31919","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7ff004c3191a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7fbdaac3191b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7fbc75c3191c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f5849c3191d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da23e1a54b7f121ac3191e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"6495294677c6ad5d39af2964","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"King Beds without Storage","description":"Elevate your bedroom with Damro’s King Beds Without Storage—designed for sleek, minimalist style without compromising on comfort or quality. Crafted in solid wood or premium upholstery, these beds offer robust support and timeless elegance—perfect for spacious and stylish bedrooms.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/20.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61326a4604b0430f2bbca","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"king-beds-without-storage","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":1,"metaTitle":"Buy King Size Beds Without Storage for Spacious Luxury Bedrooms","metaDescription":"Discover stylish king size beds without storage online. Choose modern frames and open floor designs that make your room feel larger and sophisticated.","metaKeywords":"king beds without storage, king size bed, wooden king bed, upholstered king bed, minimalist king bed, Damro beds","createdAt":"2023-06-23T05:10:30.345Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:15:39.402Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eLarge bedrooms must check the grand offerings from Damro. Our king size bed without storage will elevate your space to the next level, as the bed is designed to provide ultimate comfort and style to your bedroom. The spacious sleeping arrangement can allow the user to add throw pillows or even let your pet sleep in at times without taking up your space. Damro’s collection of king size beds has several options let’s check a few of them.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eHighly recommend king size beds without storage\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBonita king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe king-size bed without storage has a two-tone design and striking glossy finish, adding elegance to your bedroom. \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kbbt004-kd-bed-bonita-hg-m62m24-11129-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDamro’s Bonita king-size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e has a hydraulic fixture and sturdy construction, ensuring great durability for long-term usage. It is an exceptional bed with guaranteed comfort and a 36-month warranty.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBrilliant king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eAn affordable priced wooden king size bed without storage made of premium wood can elevate your bedroom. \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/nbbr004-natural-veneer-bed-brilliant-teak-2815-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDamro’s Brilliant king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e has a high headboard offering excellent support for your back and superior construction ensuring durability. The bed comes with a 12-month warranty with a modern touch on the design and finish.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEmerson king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro has introduced top quality king size bed, providing the ultimate comfort for your bedroom. \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/nbem004-natural-veneer-bed-emerson-teak-10477-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Emerson King size bed frame with no storage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e with headboard and footboard boasts elegant leather upholstery enhancing the aesthetics of the space. The bed comes with a 12-month warranty and solid wood construction ensuring long-term durability.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eZaira king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/lscwbza004-bed-zaira-king-size-bd220116-mild-natural-8683-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Zaira king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e comes with a luxurious fabric finish elevating your bedroom décor. The sturdy frame of the bed from Sheesham wood ensures stability. Damro’s well-crafted headboard design with tuft forms an excellent blend with all modern interiors. This long-lasting design topped with a lacquered finish has a 12-month warranty.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith exceptional quality and range of king-size beds without storage at affordable prices makes Damro’s collection a popular choice among buyers. Here are some of the reasons why Damro’s king size beds can adorn all homes:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuperior quality\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eSustainable and eco-friendly practices of manufacturing king-size beds. The finest quality of materials and craftsmen create a masterpiece.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAffordable pricing\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDespite the premium materials used in the making from the framework, upholstery and accessories that make the king size bed luxurious, they are exceptionally priced within your budget.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVariety of designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eVaried materials are used to design headboards and unmatched finishes for Damro’s king size beds without storage.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExcellent customer service\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe help you choose the best king size bed that matches your bedroom décor\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eand suits your needs and preferences. After-sales service and quotes for each piece of furniture are promptly provided.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can shop online or come to our nearest Damro showroom and check out the latest furniture pieces. Easy to shop and get delivery of your furniture while availing of the best offers in town and discounts of the season.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"King Size Beds Without Storage | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/king-beds-without-storage\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop king size beds without storage at Damro. Designed with premium materials, these beds offer durability and elegance for traditional and modern bedrooms.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eComfort on Damro’s king size beds without storage\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7ffc28c31920","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f2054c31921","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f6913c31922","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f2980c31923","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f6fb7c31924","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f435ec31925","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f0be1c31926","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7fef6cc31927","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f0c96c31928","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f528fc31929","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f5956c3192a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f8e17c3192b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f8de4c3192c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f615ec3192d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da240ba54b7f69a9c3192e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"60b61386a4604b0430f2bbcc","name":"Queen Beds with Storage","description":"Enhance your bedroom storage and style with Damro’s Queen Beds with Storage. Featuring smart hydraulic lifts or under-bed drawers, these beds offer ample space for linens, essentials, and seasonal items—while delivering sleek design and robust construction. Ideal for contemporary homes with an eye for both form and function.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/21.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61326a4604b0430f2bbca","ourcollection":true,"icon":"","categoryImage":"","sortValue":2,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:32:01.132Z","__v":0,"slug":"queen-beds-with-storage","enable":true,"metaDescription":"Shop queen size bed with storage options online. Choose from wooden frames, modern queen size bed designs with storage built for comfort and utility.","metaKeywords":"queen beds with storage, queen size storage bed, hydraulic queen bed, wooden queen bed with storage, Damro beds","metaTitle":"Buy Queen Size Beds With Storage Online Featuring Stylish Designs","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Queen Size Beds with Storage | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/queen-beds-with-storage\",\n  \"description\": \"Discover Damro’s collection of queen size storage beds. Featuring hydraulic and drawer storage designs, these beds combine aesthetic appeal with practical bedroom organization.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eQueen beds with storage are probably the most comfortable option for your bedroom. These modern and functional queen storage beds provide comfort, style, and sophistication. When upgrading to a new bedroom or setting up space for living in a small room, it is essential that the right queen bed is selected. Damro has given an extensive range of queen-size beds into innovative storage options to make it easy. Here is everything you will have to know before buying.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThings to note before buying queen-size beds\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCheck the room size\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAssess your bedroom space before you buy a bed of queen size. Make sure there's enough room to fit in the bed and also allow moving space and space for other furniture. Measure very well in order to avoid crowding your room with furniture.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBudget\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYour budget is important for narrowing down the options. Damro has affordable queen beds with storage and their designs fit every price range starting from 20,000 to 40,000 INR. You can buy\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/bkbs003-kd-bed-storage-m42-5737-Bengaluru\"\u003e \u003cstrong\u003eMercury Hydraulic Queen Size Storage Bed under 20,000 INR\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e. \u003c/strong\u003eFinally, pick a price that matches your financial goals without compromising on quality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStorage facility\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eQueen beds with storage, which incorporate built-in drawers or other types of storage, are ideal for homes lacking space. Finding out how much Queen-size bed with drawers will be required, choosing a design that fits your lifestyle.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBed frame and headboard\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eIt is the material and the design of the bed frame and headboard, which matters. Upholstered, wooden, or metal frames can change the appearance of your room. A design that is storage-friendly should perfectly blend into the décor of your room.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to buy storage queen bed designs online from Damro\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMeasurements and Physical Size\u003c/strong\u003e: Queen beds take a standard dimension of 60 inches in width and 80 inches in length. So, consider their measurements again, whether they would fit perfectly into your bedroom.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSize and type of mattress: While choosing a mattress, make sure it fits your bed frame. Damro has memory foam, spring, and hybrid options available for your queen bed.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStorage Facilities with the Queen Size Bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe storage arrangements can be as follows:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eQueen-size bed with drawers that would go below the bed for all the hidden storage for clothes and sheets.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eHydraulic lifts so that you can get easy access.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSide cabinets that help provide extra storage without requiring floor space and a Space-saving furniture.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuality and Durability:\u003c/strong\u003e Damro has beds in queen size made from the finest raw materials to ensure quality over time. Go in for the sturdy frames and extremely sturdy storage.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStyles with Queen Bed: \u003c/strong\u003eDecide on a modern, classic, or minimalist one that goes with your interior. Damro's designs do not fall short in offering sleek designs that take the function into aesthetic consideration.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePrice of Queen Size Bed:\u003c/strong\u003e Start comparing prices of different styles and features. Damro carries some great value-for-money products combining both luxury and affordability.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat are the available options for queen bed mattresses at Damro?\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro has different mattress sizes to suit the needs of your comfort preferences. Normally, a queen mattress measures 60 x 80 inches, yet variations include:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eSplit queen: Suited best for adjustable bed frames.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eOlympic queen: Slightly wider at 66 inches and thus provides extra space.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCustom sizes: Measured according to your specifications.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEach mattress is made to give ultimate comfort for good rest at night.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro for Queen Size Beds?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e1. Unique Designs: Queen beds like \u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kbbr007-kd-bed-briana-storage-m32m51-6102-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBriana Hydraulic Queen Size Bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e with a modern look will have storage as per the need. The designs maximize all kinds of space, style not excluded.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2. Quality Workmanship: This queen bed pattern is made specified and with the finest materials to ensure durability and elegance.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3. Affordable Pricing: Damro provides an excellent price for all the good-quality furniture they sell. There is always a discount or offer on price, which makes it much easier to find the right bed you need.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e4. Trusted Brand: As a company, Damro has a long experience of years in furniture manufacturing, which has built its image as a trusted and innovative company. With this, customer satisfaction comes as the first priority and modern queen beds with storage options are the best space-saving furniture for your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBeautify your bedroom with queen beds with storage from Damro\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eTransform your bedroom today with stylish and practical queen beds from Damro. With their extra Storage queen bed designs for your things and serving as a centerpiece for your bedroom, whatever it is you need, Damro's collection accommodates them all. Visit the whole range online and find your perfect fit!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSo much storage has now been cleverly incorporated into a bed as in Damro's new storage queen-sized beds. Whether you are redecorating a bedroom or trying to catch up on your guest room, these modern queen beds with storage options are the best options to maximize space use yet keep things stylish. There are ideal options for everyone in an impressive variety of styles, sizes, and storage arrangements.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA Queen bed with hydraulic storage in a well-organized and decluttered bedroom. The innovative designs developed by Damro, like under-bed drawers, hydraulic lift storage, and side cabinets, keep various types of storage from storing essentials like linens to seasonal clothes or personal items.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eConclusion\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAside from this, Damro wooden queen beds with storage with top-quality materials that spell many years of use and luxury experience to their clients. Affordable prices for all customization went towards making it accessible to everyone. Whether you are into ultra-modern minimalism, classic elegance, or anything in between, any of these styles would mesh well within your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eKnowing the signature of Damro for excellence, one can go ahead with confidence while shopping because it is purchasing a product that promises real value, comfort, and convenience. There is also no time for waiting to build that special bedroom-that-is-truly-you kind of space. Shop from Damro's diverse collection of queen beds with storage today and take your home further up on sophistication and orderliness.\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eChoose the Perfect Queen Size Bed with Storage for Your Home\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Beds.jpg","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b1849445b0e7b09","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/21.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Beds.jpg","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b184950d20e7b0a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b1849c6ba0e7b0b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b18491e1d0e7b0c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b18499c540e7b0d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b184948740e7b0e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b184971210e7b0f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b18496f780e7b10","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b18496ecb0e7b11","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b18496b880e7b12","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b1849c6500e7b13","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b18490ecf0e7b14","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b1849204b0e7b15","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b18490cdf0e7b16","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da27e18b1849e6f20e7b17","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"60b613aca4604b0430f2bbcd","name":"King Beds with Storage","description":"Upgrade your bedroom with Damro’s King Beds with Storage, designed to offer both comfort and smart space utilization. Featuring hydraulic lifts and under-bed drawers, these beds provide generous storage while maintaining a sleek aesthetic—ideal for modern, organized living.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/22.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61326a4604b0430f2bbca","ourcollection":false,"icon":"","categoryImage":"","sortValue":3,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:34:01.700Z","__v":0,"slug":"king-beds-with-storage","enable":true,"metaDescription":"Discover the best king size bed with storage solutions. Shop stylish designs, including wooden king size beds with storage and online options for your home.","metaKeywords":"king beds with storage, king size storage bed, hydraulic king bed, wooden king bed with storage, Damro beds","metaTitle":"Buy the Best King Size Beds With Storage Online upto @ 40% off","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"King Size Beds with Storage | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/king-beds-with-storage\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s range of king size beds with storage. Perfect for organizing your bedroom, these beds offer elegance, strength, and functionality.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eModern homes need space-saving solutions, yet want a luxurious feel to the furniture they bring to their living space. When you look out for Damro’s king size beds with storage near me,\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003ethe furniture piece provides all these features and more. Every décor or preference can be found with multiple design choices, styles and colour options to take home. The contemporary designs and durable furniture pieces can conveniently be part of every modern bedroom.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eTop king size bed with storage\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWinchester king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eGet a fully functional and durable bed to suit your bedroom space from Damro’s collection, \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kbw016-kd-bed-winchester-cushion-head-board-with-storage-m42-9175-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ea Winchester king size bed with storage.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e This elegant bed has a cushioned headboard with a melamine finish. The king size bed features a contemporary design with a hydraulic facility to lift and utilize the storage facility.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOlivia king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA spacious king size bed with a storage design can enhance your bedroom décor. The bed has a convenient hydraulic storage feature to store your extra blankets, bed linen and pillows. The space in the storage box can reduce clutter and help organize your home better. \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kbol008-kd-bed-olivia-storage-m62m24-9539-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOlivia king size bed with storage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e has a 36-month warranty has a sturdy framework and is made from high-quality engineered wood.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBriana king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen looking for the right bedroom furniture, the\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kbbr008-kd-bed-briana-storage-m32m51-6103-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e Briana king size bed with storage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e solid wood\u0026nbsp;from Damro can fit the bill. This affordable king size bed with hydraulic storage can appeal to your bedroom aesthetics. With MDF decorative panels and a two-tone melamine finish, a contemporary bed that changes your space for the better.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCarvin king size bed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuying a king size bed with hydraulic storage can help you put away essentials and save space. \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kbca008-kd-bed-carvin-storage-wgm02-1735-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCarvin king size bed with storage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e price is budget-friendly and can become an excellent addition to your home with a knockout design matching the aesthetic appeal. The hassle-free assembly at your doorstep features a king size box bed making it convenient for modern homes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eWhy choose Damro’s king size bed\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro has taken furniture making to the next level with its convenience from classic to contemporary designs catering to every preference and taste. The sturdy framework and warranty on the king size bed with storage and headboard make it a popular choice among buyers.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eUse of premium quality materials-\u0026nbsp;sustainable and eco-friendly manufacturing and sourcing of materials to make Damro king size bed with hydraulic storage.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAffordable pricing- budget-friendly price range catering to every section of buyers.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eVariety of designs- from classic to contemporary designs, a blend of both and customized options for Damro king size bed dimensions.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eExcellent customer service – the personnel at Damro assist you in picking the furniture of your choice and answering all your queries.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eAt Damro’s showrooms and online shopping, experience the extensive range of furniture. Check out the exquisite craftsmanship and designs. The high quality of the furniture can be experienced firsthand without sales assistants guiding you about the making and features of the king size beds with storage as part of the\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003eDamro hydraulic bed\u0026nbsp;collection.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover Damro’s king size bed with storage\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f5a66c319b1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7fee03c319b2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f73c7c319b3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7fced2c319b4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f0046c319b5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f2f62c319b6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f6520c319b7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f168dc319b8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7fc06ac319b9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f3569c319ba","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7fcdf7c319bb","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f81fbc319bc","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f4797c319bd","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f3e20c319be","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da2859a54b7f88eac319bf","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"64f31f96ab640c2818f163ff","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Single Beds","description":"Create a cozy and practical personal space with Damro’s Single Beds. Choose from sturdy wooden frames or smart storage models designed for compact rooms and children’s bedrooms. Built with attention to detail and durability, these beds combine comfort with space-saving style.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/23.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61326a4604b0430f2bbca","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"single-beds","lastUpdatedBy":"67922c2b9420091d5a35492c","sortValue":4,"metaTitle":"Buy daybeds online under 10,000 in india","metaDescription":"Transform compact spaces with Damro's single and daybeds. Ideal for guests, these latest designs offer comfort and eye-catching style. Elevate your room effortlessly.","metaKeywords":"single bed online, wooden single bed, storage single bed, kid’s bed, compact beds, Damro single beds","createdAt":"2023-09-02T11:42:14.572Z","updatedAt":"2025-07-07T12:27:22.619Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eStylish modern homes need to be furnished with functional furniture, Damro’s collection can comfortably accommodate every feature that a home requires. Whether you are looking for a cosy guest bed or a compact furniture piece to relax during the day, we can help you make those choices with our specially designed single bed and day beds to cater to your every need.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eCompact single beds in every room\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eSmaller bedrooms now accommodate these compact single beds without taking up much space. Even living rooms can furnish these single beds online from Damro for those living in studio apartments and needing to accommodate extra guests. Single beds also work well for children's rooms while offering comfortable sleeping solutions without compromising on style and functionality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eKey features\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ch4\u003eSpace-saving design\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe dimensions of these beds enable them to fit perfectly in compact spaces. The snug fit designs can be customized as per customer requirements and enable them to be used in smaller apartments or rooms.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eDurability\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eHigh-quality materials are used to make these single bed frames ensuring that they last long for which Damro provides a warranty.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eVariety of styles\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhether you are looking for classic or contemporary styles Damro has both and even the customized designs for your taste and preference for single bed size.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eAffordability\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003ePremium quality furniture pieces like single bed prices are budget-friendly ensuring that the customer can easily purchase and take them home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eStylish daybeds\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eDay beds have become quite popular for their versatility. Most modern homes facilitate day beds for lounging in addition to other furniture. You can find day beds in living rooms bedrooms or even in the sit outs becoming a wonderful place to relax or work.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eMultifunctional use\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eA versatile furniture piece, serving as a seating option as a daybed for the living room as well as a cosy bed at night. It can be placed in guest rooms as well as other living areas\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhy choose Damro\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro is a leading name in furniture and for several years has accomplished gaining customer trust. The brand boasts of an extensive range of furniture made of premium quality and sustainable manufacturing methods. Damro’s collection of single and day beds offers multiple options to suit every need and preference. An excellent customer service staff ensures that you pick the right daybed for your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eShop with us\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can shop with us in our showrooms across major cities or online and find an extensive collection of single and daybed designs. These furniture pieces offer practical solutions for homes that need compact furniture. The versatility of these ensures that they can be placed in any part of your home and still complement each space. They are a great addition to modern homes as they bring comfort style and functionality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Single Beds – Wooden \u0026 Storage Beds | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/single-beds\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s collection of single beds in wooden and storage variants. Ideal for kids’ rooms, guest spaces, or compact bedrooms, offering style and functionality.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eExplore the Versatility of Single and Day beds from Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b82278ebe06774","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b82281bde06775","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b822d9eae06776","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b8224439e06777","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b822250ee06778","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b822021be06779","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b822bcffe0677a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b8226092e0677b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b822f9dee0677c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b822130ae0677d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b82220aee0677e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b8228205e0677f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b822ac06e06780","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b822272fe06781","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bbd2ae1b82245bee06782","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"64f2e0baab640c7a07f16208","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Bedroom Sets","description":"Transform your bedroom into a cohesive and stylish space with Damro’s Bedroom Sets. Our curated combinations of beds, wardrobes, bedside tables, and dressers are designed to match seamlessly, offering both functionality and visual harmony. Whether you're furnishing a new home or updating your existing space, Damro's Bedroom Sets provide the perfect blend of comfort, durability, and elegant design.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/24.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61326a4604b0430f2bbca","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"bedroom-sets","lastUpdatedBy":"67922c2b9420091d5a35492c","sortValue":5,"metaTitle":"Buy Bedroom Furniture Set Online at best price | Get deals ","metaDescription":"Experience luxury with Damro's Bedroom Furniture Set. From King Beds to Wardrobes and Dressing Tables, discover the perfect blend of elegance, comfort, and style for your bedroom\n","metaKeywords":"bedroom sets, complete bedroom furniture, Bed + wardrobe set, Damro bedroom sets, matched bedroom furniture","createdAt":"2023-09-02T07:14:02.320Z","updatedAt":"2025-07-07T10:47:11.268Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eDedicated furniture sets by Damro can adorn your bedroom and transform it into a sanctuary for comfort and style. The exceptional range of bedroom sets\u0026nbsp;furniture\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003ehas both practical and durable solutions to complement any bedroom décor. Carefully crafted designs in contemporary and classic aesthetics make our collection the best choice for every perfect bedroom.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eElegance and style\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStylish designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eBoth modern and classic designs in accordance with preferred tastes, a blend of both or even customized designs form a part of our huge range of bedroom sets for sale.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Premium materials\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEco-friendly and sustainable materials go into the manufacturing processes of Damro’s bed sets collection. Buy an affordable bedroom set price for sturdy frameworks and intricately crafted furniture that lasts over several years.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Comprehensive sets\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOptimized Functionality\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSmart storage solutions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eBeds with inbuilt storage, spaciously designed wardrobes and cleverly designed storage compartments to save space in compact homes and smaller bedrooms. You can look forward to owning complete bedroom sets with wardrobe.\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eCrafting space-saving furniture to ensure your bedroom remains organized and clutter-free.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eErgonomic designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur bedroom collection includes all-round comfort and elegance. These not only work on the aesthetics front but are carefully crafted to provide ergonomically viable options in every furniture piece. Damro’s bedroom set furniture design not only provides comfort but ample support to your body to enable the best seating or sleeping experience each time.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePopular collection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eClassic elegance\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe choice of classic designs with intricate details and rich finishes adds a touch of grandeur to your bedroom set Damro. The look of elegance brings back the old-world charm as the classic looks of the furniture pieces are recreated by our craftsman. Buying traditional bedroom set designs from Damro can add timeless beauty to the entire space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Minimalistic charm\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnderstated elegance with subtle hues forms modern décor and complements your bedroom. The clean lines and minimalistic designs add a touch of sophistication. Damro bed with storage has created sleek designs, neutral colours and functional elements that reflect your style to create a contemporary ambiance.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;Rustic vibes\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe warmth and coziness of the rustic designs are unbeatable. Use natural wood and earthy tones to create a perfect relaxed atmosphere for the vibe of the countryside in your very own bedroom. You can check out other additional pieces to add to your bedroom with Damro furniture price list.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eExplore Damro bedroom set price has a stylish collection befitting all home décor. With functional and durable options in various colours, finishes, materials and dimensions to complement your taste and spaces. You check out elegant furniture pieces at our showrooms or online stores, each uniquely designed to provide practicality and comfort to your bedrooms.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Dining Table Sets - 4, 6 \u0026 8 Seater | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/dining-sets\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s wide range of dining sets including 4-seater, 6-seater, and 8-seater options. Designed for comfort and elegance, ideal for modern Indian homes.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eTransform your space with Bedroom sets from Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b0ac0e47dff","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b8eece47e00","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b0c45e47e01","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877bff98e47e02","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b67e9e47e03","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b0796e47e04","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b98f3e47e05","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877bdfaae47e06","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b3f97e47e07","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b91e0e47e08","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b7e66e47e09","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b2958e47e0a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b0802e47e0b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b6ed7e47e0c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686ba5af5b877b5123e47e0d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null}]},{"_id":"64f1b8c3ab640c306ef15bb2","name":"Dresser and Bedside Tables","slug":"dresser-and-bedside-tables","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Dresser and Sode Tables.jpg","icon":"","description":"Elevate your bedroom with Damro’s Dressers \u0026 Bedside Tables, designed to combine elegance with practicality. Featuring spacious drawers and chic finishes, these pieces offer ideal storage for essentials and add a coordinated look when paired with our beds and wardrobes. Perfect for creating a neat, stylish, and comfortable sleep space.","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Dressers \u0026 Bedside Tables | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/dresser-and-bedside-tables\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s collection of stylish dressers and bedside tables. Designed for modern bedrooms, they offer smart storage with elegant finishes.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"60b61600a4604b0430f2bbd3","name":"Dressing Tables","description":"Elevate your bedroom’s aesthetic and utility with Damro’s Dressing Tables. Each unit combines a beautifully framed mirror with convenient storage drawers—perfect for organizing cosmetics, jewelry, and accessories. Choose from modern and classic designs to create a graceful, personalised vanity space.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/25.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"64f1b8c3ab640c306ef15bb2","ourcollection":false,"icon":"","categoryImage":"","sortValue":0,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-07-07T11:28:02.967Z","__v":0,"slug":"dressing-tables","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eEvery piece of furniture including the dressing tables needs to blend with the aesthetics and enhance the beauty of the space they occupy. A dressing table from Damro can make a style statement while complementing your bedroom décor. The design and functionality of the dressing table make it a practical addition to your space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeatures of perfect dressing tables\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTimeless elegance\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eClassic designs and the blend of contemporary detailing complete the well-crafted pieces. Premium materials ensure sturdy construction and durability of the dressing table with mirror and storage. A timeless elegance to every dressing table crafted with a sophisticated finish complements your taste and preference.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFunctional design\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe elegance and convenience of a well-crafted dressing table fit into Damro's functional design. These dressing tables have ample storage space options to ensure clutter-free spaces. With several shelves and drawers to easily organize accessories, cosmetics, jewellery and other items, the dressing table design is a great space-saving solution for many homes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePremium quality\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eSustainable and eco-friendly materials are sourced and manufactured in-house by Damro. Each dressing table with mirror is crafted with care and premium materials to ensure lasting usage. \u0026nbsp;Sleek finishes and excellence in detail showcase superior craftsmanship. Every piece of furniture is quality-tested and comes with a warranty.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore options\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDepending on your space restrictions, design, colour and finish options, We make compact or luxe pieces of furniture that complement every home décor, befitting your taste and requirements.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTrusted brand\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOver several years, Damro has captured the mind and space of many homes with our furniture brand. Having locally sourced the materials and ensured local craftsmen work on our furniture pieces like the dressing table organizer to provide the best indigenous artistry to our customers. We understand better both the trends and customer’s needs and strive to bring excellence to every product through innovative designs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWide range of collections\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eAn extensive collection of furniture pieces with all the colours, design and finish options. The evergreen classic options or the blend of modern contribute to a long list of options customers appreciate. Damro’s bedroom range of dressing tables with storage, mirrors, and drawers including other options with combinations are available.\u0026nbsp; We cater from elaborate styles to minimalist designs as well as customized options ensuring every taste and preference is delivered.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExceptional customer service\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur knowledgeable and friendly staff ensure you pick the right dressing table to adorn your home, satisfying your every requirement. They help you pick an ideal dressing table price that matches your budget. With our expert guidance and support, you can experience seamless shopping for your ideal furniture piece.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eInvest in a functional dressing table to transform your bedroom space. The dressing table under 10,000\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003ehas an elegant design and provides a luxurious experience at affordable pricing from Damro.\u0026nbsp; You can shop online or at our showroom and check out the various furniture pieces from our catalogue.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","metaDescription":"Chest of Drawers - Buy Wooden Chest of Drawers Online in India. Choose from Latest Wooden Chester drawer furniture for bedroom \u0026 Get ⭐No Cost EMI ⭐Free Shipping Across India\n","metaKeywords":"dressing tables, dressing table with mirror, makeup vanity, wooden dressing table, bedroom dressing furniture, Damro dressing tables","metaTitle":"Chest of Drawers - Buy Wooden Chest of Drawers Online in India | Damro","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Dressing Tables | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/dressing-tables\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s dressing tables crafted for modern bedrooms. Featuring mirrors and storage drawers, these units bring style and utility to your daily routine.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eElegant dressing tables from Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"67922c2b9420091d5a35492c","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a5553918c53961e6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a5553925463961e7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a55539b33b3961e8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a555397ec53961e9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a555390a423961ea","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a555392a193961eb","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a55539036f3961ec","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a55539578d3961ed","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a5553970403961ee","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a5553992713961ef","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a5553929733961f0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a555397de33961f1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a5553962273961f2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a55539f3b13961f3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baf42a555392f8f3961f4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"6294b1ba4d9f7f3d5895ad00","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Bedside Tables","description":"Enhance your bedroom’s functionality and style with Damro’s bedside tables. Our collection features sleek wooden designs with built-in drawers and practical storage solutions—ideal for keeping essentials close and adding a polished finish to your sleep space.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/26.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"64f1b8c3ab640c306ef15bb2","icon":"","slug":"bedside-tables","sortValue":1,"metaTitle":"Night Stands: Buy Night Stands Online in India @ Best Price","metaDescription":"Buy Night Stands Online At Upto 20%. Shop Latest Range of Nightstands Online In India. ✯Free Shipping ✯New Arrivals ✯Low Cost EMI ✯High Quality Product\n","metaKeywords":"bedside tables, nightstands, wooden bedside tables, storage bedside units, bedroom bedside furniture, Damro bedside tables","createdAt":"2022-05-30T11:59:54.547Z","updatedAt":"2025-07-07T11:08:17.483Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eBedside tables are a great addition to your bedroom. Functional and aesthetic pieces of furniture complementing your décor from Damro cannot be neglected. Made from engineered wood, these bedside tables can easily be assembled and dismantled as required when on the go. These bedside tables\u0026nbsp;provide the most practical storage solutions while enhancing the style and functionality of your bedroom.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeatures of bedside table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStylish designs\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEvery bedside table design marks the artistry of the craftsmen at Damro. From classic to contemporary styles make up our showroom. Each intricate detailing and elegant finishes blend with your space while adding a touch of sophistication. A range of designs and customization options to pick from modern or minimalistic designs according to your taste and preferences.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFunctional storage solutions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eSmaller homes and apartments can utilize bedside tables as great storage options. Multiple drawers and shelves give ample space to store all your essentials within reach. Organize bedroom spaces with a bedside table with drawer to accommodate place books, lamps, personal items, and phones among other things.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuality craftsmanship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eUnmatched craftsmanship at Damro can ensure you the best quality materials used to make the modern bedside table design with durable quality for regular usage. Sustainable and high-quality manufacturing processes ensure the longevity of the furniture piece. The sturdy construction ensures the bedside tables require hardly any maintenance with an enduring aesthetic appeal.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore options\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you have specific requirements in dimensions, finish, colour, or design. We provide made-to-deliver\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003ebedside table Damro that suit your preferences and tastes. Our tailor-made option will ensure your bedside table reflects your personal style and specific needs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ewhy choose Damro\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReputable brand\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro is a well-known brand with a high-quality furniture range. We understand the evolving furniture trends and know customer requirements, propelling us to develop innovative designs to fulfil the diverse needs of our customers. They have affordable and high-quality\u003cstrong\u003e \u003c/strong\u003ebedside tables for small space\u0026nbsp;to spacious homes. \u0026nbsp;We have furniture pieces that every home can invest in styling their spaces.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExtensive collection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur showrooms across the country and online shopping spaces have an extensive collection of every design, colour, material, dimension, finish and other addition. Whether you prefer classic, modern, or a blend of both, we match your preferences with ideal bedside table wooden\u0026nbsp;décor ready to occupy your space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExceptional customer service\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s team of trained personnel will assist you in selecting the ideal bedside table for sale at our showroom, ensuring a seamless shopping experience. The support from our staff will provide expert guidance in maintenance and functionality before being delivered to your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuying bedside tables ensures your space gets a stylish and functional furniture piece. It also serves as a practical solution to transform your bedroom. You can explore our extensive bedside table options at discounted prices and browse the modern collection from Damro. The premium quality materials provide a luxurious feel to the affordably priced bedside tables. Investing in a bedside table from Damro can ensure quality, durable, and long-lasting furniture\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Bedside Tables – Nightstands with Storage | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/bedside-tables\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s collection of wooden bedside tables with storage drawers. Stylish and space-saving options to complement your bedroom furniture.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eStylish bedside tables by Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"67922c2b9420091d5a35492c","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555397134396165","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a55539108f396166","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555398109396167","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555391ca5396168","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555392e45396169","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a55539cc1039616a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555395f4039616b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a55539a33b39616c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555392e8439616d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a55539555439616e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555391dd539616f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555399522396170","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555397dbe396171","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a555397d8d396172","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686baaa1a5553997d2396173","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null}]},{"_id":"60b61566a4604b0430f2bbd0","name":"Wardrobes","slug":"wardrobes","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Wardrobes.jpg","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/6 Wardrobe.jpg","description":"Explore Damro’s versatile range of wardrobes, featuring sliding and swing-door designs in 2‑, 3‑, and 4‑door options. Find the perfect match for your bedroom storage needs.\n\n","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Wardrobes – Sliding \u0026 Swing-Door Options | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/wardrobes\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s collection of wardrobes online. Featuring durable and stylish sliding and swing-door designs in 2-, 3-, and 4-door configurations.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"649536ec77c6ad2748af317d","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Two Door Wardrobes","description":"Discover Damro’s compact 2-door wardrobes, perfect for small bedrooms and efficient storage. Choose from swing-door and sliding-door styles with sleek finishes and durable build.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/27.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61566a4604b0430f2bbd0","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"two-door-wardrobes","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":0,"metaTitle":"Buy Two Door Wardrobes with Modern Wood Designs for Style","metaDescription":"Choose versatile two door wardrobes for your space. Find modern two door wardrobe styles and two door wooden wardrobes crafted to combine style and durability.","metaKeywords":"2 door wardrobes, two door wardrobe, compact wardrobe, small bedroom wardrobes, swing door wardrobe, sliding door wardrobe, Damro wardrobes","createdAt":"2023-06-23T06:08:44.586Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:17:42.182Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eEvery room in the house requires storage space that conveniently fits your lifestyle. Each furniture piece needs to establish its purpose and blend in fulfilling its functionality. Damro’s extremely stylish and spacious \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kwad001-wardrobe-andriana-with-sliding-door-m42m41-7791-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003etwo-door wardrobes\u003c/strong\u003e f\u003c/a\u003eor your home become your practical storage solution. From meeting aesthetic preferences to storage needs, our ideal wardrobe complements your bedroom décor and enhances it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeatures of two-door wardrobes\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eElegant designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur craftsmen have worked on making unique and timeless designs while incorporating classic, modern and minimalist styles to match every taste. We provide customized designs to suit your preferences and style. Each detail and intricate pattern add to the aesthetic appeal of the two-door wardrobe design. Damro’s collection ensures a suitable addition to your bedroom while complementing your requirements.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuperior quality\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/bkwb008-wardrobe-with-2-doors--mirror-m42-5727-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003equality two-door wardrobe\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e interior design is unmatchable in terms of style and elegance. The usage of premium quality materials and sturdy construction ensure a lifetime of durability. With robust and excellent craftsmanship showcase fine detailing to complement your bedroom décor and enhance your space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAmple storage space\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe two-door wardrobe size ensures ample storage space without compromising on the style quotient. These wardrobes have spacious compartments, shelves and hanging rails to organise your clothes and accessories. Owning these elegant furniture pieces in your bedroom keeps your essentials organised and spaces decluttered.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVersatility\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s versatile two-door wardrobe with mirror allows it to fit into various spaces from the master bedroom to smaller guest rooms at your home. Made from engineered wood, these wardrobes come with a warranty. The compact and spacious designs make them suitable for any room size while offering practical storage solutions without taking up too much space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch2\u003eWhy choose Damro\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTrusted brand\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eA reputable furniture brand, Damro has delivered high-quality and innovative functional furniture for several years. We use sustainable and eco-friendly manufacturing processes while promoting indigenous artistry. Locally sourced premium quality materials are utilized to make exquisite pieces of furniture including two-door wardrobe with drawers. With our exceptional craftsmen, we meet the diverse needs of customers and provide exclusive designs and finishes for every product.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWide range of collection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe extensive collection covers all classic, contemporary, minimalist, blend of styles, innovative and customized options. These furniture pieces like two-door wardrobe with mirror and drawers\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003ealso come in various colours, finishes, dimensions and other features.\u0026nbsp; Damro’s collection can fit every home and complete any décor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExcellent customer service\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eCustomer satisfaction is our priority while we help you pick an ideal two-door wardrobe with shelves that complement your home and bedroom. Our knowledgeable staff ensures that you get expert guidance and support for a seamless shopping experience at Damro.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuying a two-door wardrobe\u0026nbsp;from Damro can transform your space and offer both elegance and practicality. It is a great solution to organizing personal belongings by having a dedicated space to arrange and protect them. You can check all our offers and collections at our showroom or shop online to discover the perfect wardrobe for your bedroom.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"2‑Door Wardrobes – Compact \u0026 Stylish | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/two-door-wardrobes\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s range of 2‑door wardrobes ideal for compact bedrooms and efficient storage. Available in swing and sliding door designs with durable finishes.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover the spacious two-door wardrobes from Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04740c04a97e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04ba1904a97f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e0409b604a980","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04cf3f04a981","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04f78f04a982","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04447f04a983","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04aeda04a984","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04f1dc04a985","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04135a04a986","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e042ef104a987","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04d86a04a988","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e0410d804a989","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04509c04a98a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04376604a98b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24867a7e04a09404a98c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"6495372d77c6ad0ff7af3180","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Three Door Wardrobes","description":"Enhance your bedroom’s storage and style with Damro’s Three‑Door Wardrobes. These versatile units offer spacious interiors with hanging sections, shelves, and drawers—available in both swing and sliding door variants. Crafted with durable materials and elegant finishes, they seamlessly blend functionality and aesthetics for modern living spaces.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/28.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61566a4604b0430f2bbd0","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"three-door-wardrobes","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":1,"metaTitle":"Buy Three Door Wardrobes Online with Smart Storage Solutions","metaDescription":"Explore stylish three door wardrobes with lasting quality. Choose three door wooden wardrobes designed to maximize space and suit modern bedroom interiors.","metaKeywords":"3 door wardrobes, three door wardrobes, bedroom wardrobes, swing-door wardrobes, sliding wardrobes, Damro wardrobes","createdAt":"2023-06-23T06:09:49.829Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:18:05.648Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eWhen looking to store your clothing, accessories and essentials, a bigger storage space can make life much easier, when you have a \u003cstrong\u003eDamro’s three-door wardrobe\u003c/strong\u003e. Buying a wardrobe having a perfect combination of aesthetics and functionality can enhance your home. It can help curate your belongings in an organized manner and keep your space clutter-free. Discover the perfect wardrobe that blends into your bedroom décor and manage your space efficiently.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeatures of Damro’s three-door wardrobes\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eElegant designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eA variety of three-door wardrobe design and styles suiting different tastes and interior themes for your spaces are part of Damro’s collection. Whether it is modern, classic, minimalistic or a blend of several styles to match your home décor and taste, we have it all as part of our collection.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpacious storage designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro has a versatile range of three-door wardrobes with drawers enabling you to store clothes, essentials and accessories in an organized manner. With ample space in the form of multiple shelves, drawers and hanging rails you can access things easily. These wardrobes has spacious designed layouts and aesthetically designed exteriors to complement your bedroom funishings.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHigh-quality craftsmanship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003ePremium quality and locally sourced materials and eco-friendly manufacturing processes are used to make stylish \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kwca003-wardrobe-carvin-with-3-doors-wgm02-2224-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3 door wardrobe\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/a\u003e Our expert craftsman works on exquisite design and detailing to ensure stylish wardrobes adorn your bedrooms. The use of engineered wood and protective PVC edges to ensure durability. Damro’s robust construction and framework provide a warranty period for their products.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFunctional features\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEvery wardrobe, not only serves as a storage option but comes with additional features of mirrored doors increasing its utility. The practical design and layouts of the \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kwke004-wardrobe-keegan-with-3-doors-mirror-m42m41-6234-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ethree-door wardrobe with mirror\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e enable it to store every kind of clothing among other things.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTrusted brand\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eA reputable brand in the furniture industry, Damro has delivered excellent quality and innovative designs for several years. With sustainable products and eco-friendly manufacturing processes, Damro’s three-door wardrobe has satisfied the diverse needs of customers by providing innovative furniture solutions.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExtensive collection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s 3-door wardrobe designs for bedroom is available in various sizes, colours, finishes and materials. You can customize the design and layout for the number of shelves drawers and hanging rails in the wardrobe to suit your needs. Our easy-to-find collections and innovative wardrobe designs ensure you have a seamless shopping experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExcellent customer service\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe prioritise customer satisfaction by delivering an affordable and premium collection of our \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/bkwb009-wardrobe-with-3-doors-and-inside-drawer-m42-5657-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e3 door wardrobes under 30000\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/a\u003e Damro’s products maintain high quality, durability and aesthetic appeal for years to come. Our knowledgeable staff assists you in finding the perfect wardrobe to take home.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuying a three-door wardrobe from Damro is a perfect investment for your home. The product comes with a warranty and low maintenance even with regular usage. Browse into our 3 door wardrobe designs catalogue to check out our online and showroom furniture collection. We help transform your space while offering both elegance and practicality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Three-Door Wardrobes – Stylish Bedroom Storage | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/three-door-wardrobes\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s collection of three-door wardrobes, offering ample storage and aesthetic designs. Available in both swing and sliding-door formats for modern bedrooms.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eBring in three-door wardrobe from Damro to furnish your bedroom\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f0538c31940","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f4d15c31941","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f4c81c31942","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f80dfc31943","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f9c3dc31944","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f1bfbc31945","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f2223c31946","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f125fc31947","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f7333c31948","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f8d93c31949","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f0656c3194a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f1a6bc3194b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7fc819c3194c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f686ec3194d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da249da54b7f4b1fc3194e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"6495375977c6adaf61af3183","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Four Door Wardrobes","description":"Upgrade your bedroom storage with Damro’s Four‑Door Wardrobes. These roomy and stylish units offer multiple compartments, hanging areas, and shelves—ideal for organizing clothes, accessories, and linens. Built with premium materials and a range of attractive finishes, they blend seamlessly into modern interiors.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/29.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61566a4604b0430f2bbd0","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"four-door-wardrobes","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":2,"metaTitle":"Buy Four Door Wardrobes in Stylish Design for Wood Homes","metaDescription":"Upgrade your storage with four door wardrobes featuring modern four door wardrobe design. Shop online for pieces built with quality wood and smart layout.","metaKeywords":"4 door wardrobe, four door wardrobe, large wardrobe, wardrobe with sliding doors, swing door wardrobe, Damro wardrobes","createdAt":"2023-06-23T06:10:33.117Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:18:28.142Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eGet home the sophisticated charm with Damro’s four-door wardrobes. Each design has been carefully crafted to blend with your taste and style. With a sturdy framework, it can meet all your storage requirements while adding a touch of elegance to your bedroom. Made from engineered wood, soft edge shutters and sturdy handles ensure optimal user experience. Our furniture pieces provide excellent designs that showcase both style and functionality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFeatures of Damro’s four door wardrobes\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExquisite designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe classic elegant styling to modern sleek designs forms a big part of the exquisite collection at Damro. \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/kwca004-wardrobe-carvin-with-4-doors-wgm02-2225-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBuying four-door wardrobes\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e takes care of your diverse storage needs and can become part of any room at your home with big capacity shelves enabling you to store all your items.\u0026nbsp; With various finishes of wood or melamine to personalized styles, we ensure to complement your room interiors, enabling you to reflect your personal style with our four-door wardrobe with mirror.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpacious storage solutions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s four-door wardrobe design offers ample space to organize your things. The design provides spacious storage shelves, drawers and other compartments to keep your living area tidy and clutter-free. The design of the compartments in the wardrobes ensures to hold a lot more without having to cram up your stuff and have access easily\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePremium quality\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eUsing high-grade and locally sourced materials, \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/nwbr01-natural-veneer-wardrobe-brilliant-4-door-teak-9627-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDamro’s four-door wardrobe\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e size is designed by expert craftsmen with intricate artistry. Our thoughtfully designed storage solution can stand the test of time because of its durability and robust construction. Experience the elegance and strength of the meticulously curated wardrobe adorning your spaces.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTrusted brand\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro has established a reputation in premium quality furniture and an innovative design range for four-door wardrobe price.\u0026nbsp; Expert craftsmen who ensure robust construction and intricate detailing go into the making of Damro’s unique products. Our brand has years of experience in manufacturing eco-friendly and sustainable furniture pieces. We provide furniture solutions that focus on reliability and style.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExtensive collection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can find wardrobe designs in various colours, finishes, makes and dimensions apart from this, Damro provides customised versions as well to suit your needs and preferences. Classic, modern and minimalistic designs are part of extensive collections or blends of many to create unique and innovative styles that form a part of Damro’s four-door wardrobe with drawers range. With exclusive offers for various furniture pieces, we ensure you have a seamless and enjoyable shopping experience at Damro.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExceptional customer service\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eCustomer satisfaction at Damro is paramount as we ensure all our products get rigorously tested for quality. We help you pick the ideal \u0026nbsp;4 door wardrobe complementation of your preference and home décor with personalized assistance. Our products provide a warranty and assurance of low maintenance at affordable pricing.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s elegant \u0026nbsp;4 door wardrobes for sale can transform your home; to find various designs and other details you can browse our catalogue or visit our online store or showrooms for more options. Pick out the ideal wardrobes, offering the perfect blend of style, functionality and quality to make your home beautifully organized.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Four Door Wardrobes | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/four-door-wardrobes\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore spacious and stylish 4 door wardrobes at Damro. Perfect for organizing clothes, accessories, and more while enhancing your bedroom's look.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover the elegant four-door wardrobes from Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7fa9f2c31950","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f1ed5c31951","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f3c3fc31952","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7faec9c31953","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f131cc31954","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7fb6d4c31955","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f46e4c31956","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f1879c31957","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f1ed7c31958","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f9a4fc31959","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7fc31bc3195a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f944dc3195b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f70efc3195c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f4afec3195d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da24b4a54b7f3571c3195e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null}]},{"_id":"60b615a6a4604b0430f2bbd1","name":"Storage and Accessories","slug":"storage-accessories","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/chest of drowars.jpg","icon":"","description":"Declutter with style using Damro’s Storage Accessories. Featuring versatile solutions like baskets, drawer organizers, compartment trays, and stackable containers—perfect for kitchens, wardrobes, study areas, and more. Enhance your storage space with functional and aesthetic pieces crafted for modern living.\n\n","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Storage Accessories \u0026 Organizers | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/storage-accessories\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s storage accessories collection including drawer organizers, closet storage boxes, and compact units—designed to help you declutter and organize your home efficiently.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"6375ddada2d9b3dbc46df704","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Chest Of Drawers","description":"Organize your space seamlessly with Damro’s Chest of Drawers collection. Crafted from quality wood and finished for elegance, these multi-drawer cabinets offer practical storage for clothing, linens, and daily essentials—perfect for bedrooms, living rooms, or hallways.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/chest of drowars.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b615a6a4604b0430f2bbd1","icon":"","slug":"chest-of-drawers","sortValue":1,"metaTitle":"Buy chest of drawers online in India ","metaDescription":"Are you looking for a sturdy chest of drawers for storage purposes? This engineered wood chest of drawers for the bedroom or living room has spacious drawers to keep essential items. Shop now from Damro ","metaKeywords":"chest of drawers, wooden drawers, bedroom storage, drawer cabinets, storage furniture, Damro chest of drawers","createdAt":"2022-11-17T07:07:25.849Z","updatedAt":"2025-07-07T11:12:30.950Z","__v":0,"seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Chest of Drawers – Wooden Storage Units | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/chest-of-drawers\",\n  \"description\": \"Discover Damro’s stylish and functional chest of drawers. Perfect for organizing your bedroom or living space with ample storage and elegant finishes.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eLiving spaces can look way better with an elegant \u003cstrong\u003echest of drawers from Damro\u003c/strong\u003e. These functional storage accessories enhance your home décor while providing functionality and style.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eElegant designs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eClassic and contemporary styles\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s \u003cstrong\u003echest of wooden drawers \u003c/strong\u003ecrafted to perfection in various designs and styles that complement every home’s interiors. Whether you prefer our classic designs or the contemporary styles, in various dimensions and finishes.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePremium Materials\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cstrong\u003echest of drawers \u003c/strong\u003eis made from premium materials. Crafted by expert artisans providing attention to detail on the framework to the finishing touch. The sturdy construction makes it a durable furniture piece with a warranty from Damro.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFunctional storage solutions\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAmple storage space\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuying a Damro’s \u003cstrong\u003echest of drawers online\u003c/strong\u003e in any of your rooms makes for an excellent storage solution.\u0026nbsp;A great way to declutter your home and get things organized in a designated space allowing you to find them easily. These compact chests of drawers can hold a lot of items and not take up much space in your room.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSmooth drawer mechanism\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe drawers are designed with smooth-glide mechanisms allowing easy access without struggling to open or close each time you need to get something out of them. The sturdy construction of the chest of drawers ensures it remains in the best condition despite regular usage.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVersatile use\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eBedroom essential\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eUse the drawers to store clothing and accessories in your bedroom among other things. Damro’s \u003cstrong\u003echest of drawers dresser\u003c/strong\u003e can be ordered to match your wardrobe and other bedroom furniture to complement your bedroom décor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLiving room and hallway\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlacing these \u003cstrong\u003echests of drawers traditional\u003c/strong\u003e in any corner of the house whether in the living room, hallway or other place, can enhance any space. Using the countertop to place vases or decorative items, or stack books, the chest of drawers adds utility and elegance to your home in every form.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore options\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFinishes and colours\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eWe have classic shades and modern colour palettes for our chest of drawers. However, personalized choices to match your home décor are specially crafted by our artisans. A blending of contemporary and minimalistic styles in the finish and colour schemes makes our collection more extensive than any \u003cstrong\u003efurniture store near you\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eQuality and craftsmanship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro, a reputable brand for several years has managed to provide assured quality and craftsmanship to its customers. Whether it's home or office we have a \u003cstrong\u003echest of drawers for the living room\u003c/strong\u003e crafted to perfection in both detailing and design. The use of superior materials and artistry ensures the incredible standards of durability and functionality of every piece of furniture.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCustomer satisfaction\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith our exceptional quality and extensive range of furniture, customers can buy affordably priced products of their choice and get \u003cstrong\u003echest of drawers\u003c/strong\u003e. Our knowledgeable and friendly staff ensures you choose an ideal item for your home within your budget, matching your preferences and complementing your home décor.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eGet the best home furniture from Damro, shop online or visit our store for any furniture requirement. Browse our catalogues to pick the perfect \u003cstrong\u003echest of drawers for sale\u003c/strong\u003e from our collection to be delivered to your home.\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eA Blend of Style and Utility with Damro’s Chest of Drawers\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"67922c2b9420091d5a35492c","homeCategoryImg":"","categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null,"regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e0367669b76d9676e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e0367666113d9676f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e036766d142d96770","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e0367660968d96771","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e036766261cd96772","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e0367665544d96773","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e03676654d8d96774","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e036766437fd96775","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e036766cd5ed96776","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e03676699f9d96777","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e0367668b89d96778","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e036766d4a7d96779","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e0367665ea1d9677a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e036766a4dcd9677b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bab9e03676645a9d9677c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}]}]},{"_id":"60b6180ba4604b0430f2bbd7","name":"Mattresses","slug":"mattresses","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Mattresses.jpg","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/7 Mattress.jpg","description":"Upgrade your sleep quality with Damro’s premium mattress range. Choose from memory foam, coir, and spring options in single, queen, and king sizes—all designed for optimal comfort, spinal alignment, and lasting performance. Find the perfect mattress to support restful nights and refreshed mornings.\n\n","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Buy Mattresses Online – Coir, Spring \u0026 Foam | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/mattresses\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s mattress collection including memory foam, coir, and spring mattresses. Available in multiple sizes for enhanced comfort and support.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"62849ae75f1d6f62c3d08b52","ourcollection":true,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Queen Size Mattresses","description":"Upgrade your sleep with Damro’s Queen Size Mattresses. Available in memory foam for pressure relief, coir for natural support, and spring for classic resilience each mattress is crafted for comfort, durability, and superior spine alignment. Perfectly sized for your bed frame and loved by sleepers of all kinds.\n\n","image":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/31.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b6180ba4604b0430f2bbd7","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","slug":"queen-size-mattresses","sortValue":0,"metaTitle":"Buy Queen Size Mattresses with best Materials upto 35% off","metaDescription":"Upgrade your sleep with queen size mattresses made from memory foam, pocket springs, or hybrid layers. Buy online for quality and long-lasting comfort.","metaKeywords":"queen size mattress, memory foam queen mattress, coir queen mattress, spring queen mattress, queen bed mattress, Damro mattresses","createdAt":"2022-05-18T07:06:15.731Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:37:18.465Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eDiscover luxurious sleep accessories from Damro provide unmatched support and comfort. Our queen-size mattresses offer the ultimate sleep experience. Expert craftsmanship using sustainable and premium materials to achieve the perfect balance between softness and support ensuring a good night’s sleep. Combining innovative design and ergonomic features we ensure you get a night of restful relaxation.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eInnovative materials\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur mattresses are crafted with memory foam to provide superior comfort and support. The layers conform to the body’s shape and minimize pressure points ensuring any sleep discomforts are no longer bothering you. The pocket springs in the mattress reduce motion transfer caused by individual body movements enabling minimized disturbances during sleep. Since latex is naturally sourced, can provide breathability, bounce and durability to the queen-size mattress for sale from Damro.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eErgonomic design\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDesigned to provide ample support and promote proper spinal alignment. The ergonomic design for Damro’s queen-size mattress dimensions ensures reduced pressure points offering optimal support and comfort while you sleep. When you want to elevate your sleep experience, buy Damro’s mattress with a soft top and preferential thickness for greater comfort and feel.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurability and quality\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe use of premium materials and superior craftsmanship ensure your queen-size mattress is durable for many years providing consistent comfort even after regular use. With robust construction and design, the shape and support of the mattress don’t change over time providing long-lasting performance. Damro’s queen-size mattress offers a comprehensive warranty for your purchase reflecting our commitment to the highest standards of quality.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHealth and hygiene\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo minimize the allergens and prevent triggers, the designed hypoallergenic properties in the queen-size mattress support a healthier sleeping environment. Using breathable fabrics for designing Damro’s \u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/lcmd78604-dura-coir-mattress-maroon-2490-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003equeen-size mattress under 15000\u003c/strong\u003e,\u003c/a\u003e ensures that you get to enjoy fresh, well-ventilated sleep spaces and reduce heat buildup.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMore Selection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuyers can opt for a variety of firmness levels and cozy queen-size mattresses, according to their comfort levels. Individualistic choices of plush feel or firmer surface as per sleep preferences. The high-quality finishes ensure elegant designs, making Damro’s queen-size mattress designs both stylish and functional.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro's queen-size mattress\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExceptional craftsmanship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEach mattress has exceptional craftsmanship ensuring the highest standards of quality. \u0026nbsp;Stylish and functional furniture options from Damro can add a touch of sophistication to every home. Experts craft with meticulous precision the detailing and sturdy frame of the \u003cstrong\u003equeen-size mattress deals\u003c/strong\u003e to ensure a long-lasting experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCustomer satisfaction\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s staff ensures you pick the ideal \u003cstrong\u003equeen-size mattress near me\u003c/strong\u003e for your bedroom while fitting into your budget. We provide a seamless shopping experience while our dedicated team offers to provide with outstanding service and support. Warranty is guaranteed by Damro on its queen-size mattress to instil confidence in your purchase and offer you peace of mind.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop us online\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can look forward to experiencing unparalleled comfort with Damro’s \u003cstrong\u003equeen-size mattress delivery\u003c/strong\u003e from our online store or showrooms. You can contact our customer service team or visit our website to explore the collection, pick the perfect mattress, and ensure complete satisfaction.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Queen Size Mattresses – Memory Foam, Coir \u0026 Spring | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/queen-size-mattresses\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop queen size mattresses at Damro in memory foam, coir, and spring types. Designed for comfort, durability, and a good night’s sleep.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eUnparalleled Support for Queen-Size Mattresses From Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Mattress.jpg","categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null,"regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b18494bb10e7b19","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/31.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Mattress.jpg","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b1849250d0e7b1a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Mattress.jpg","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b184934410e7b1b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b18497f710e7b1c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b184922760e7b1d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b1849edf10e7b1e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b184957a00e7b1f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b18495f700e7b20","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Mattress.jpg","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b1849177c0e7b21","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Mattress.jpg","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b18497d3f0e7b22","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b18498ed40e7b23","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b1849754c0e7b24","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b184931060e7b25","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b184978730e7b26","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Mattress.jpg","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da291e8b18490eb10e7b27","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/icon.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Mattress.jpg","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f","offer":""}]},{"_id":"60b61858a4604b0430f2bbd9","name":"King Size Mattresses","description":"Enhance your sleep quality with Damro’s King Size Mattresses. Available in premium memory foam, coir, and spring variations, these mattresses are engineered for optimal comfort, durability, and body support. Perfectly sized for larger bedrooms, they offer an indulgent sleep experience night after night.\n\n","image":"","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b6180ba4604b0430f2bbd7","ourcollection":false,"icon":"","categoryImage":"","sortValue":1,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:22:46.580Z","__v":0,"slug":"king-size-mattresses","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eWhen looking for ultimate relaxation you can count on, Damro’s king-size mattresses. Made to cater for every taste and preference, offering unparalleled comfort and support, this mattress ensures you live life the king-size.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eUnmatched comfort and support\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor restful nights and rejuvenated mornings, Damro’s king-size mattresses provide exceptional comfort. We understand your unique sleep needs while crafting the mattresses with premium materials and ergonomic design. It can be a perfect addition to your bedroom and ensure you a good night’s sleep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAdvanced materials\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMemory foam\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe foam ensures the king-size mattress conforms to the body shape. It enables you to relieve the pressure on the body and evoke personalized comfort as you sleep. Since the mattress adapts to your body making it a custom fit for every night, you can experience waking up refreshed.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLatex\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro uses Latex as an eco-friendly and natural material yet offers the king-size mattress price affordable to our customers. These offer resilience and breathability ensuring a cooler environment to sleep in. The mattress provides excellent support and durability with a natural bounce from the latex.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePocket springs\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe pocket springs in the king-size mattress dimensions\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003efrom Damro provide individualized support and respond to your body movements. As a user, you can experience the smooth motion transfer for a stable and restful sleep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eErgonomic design\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eEvery Damro king-size mattress has ergonomically designed features to provide proper spinal support to reduce pressure points. The perfect design ensures minimized disturbances and peaceful sleep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eLong-lasting quality\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMade from premium materials endures regular usage and the product comes with a warranty. The robust construction and meticulous craftsmanship of Damro’s king-size mattress frame have given durability and comfort for several years.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePersonalized options\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can pick from the variety of firmness levels at our showroom and take the perfect fit home. Providing comfort may be the main feature, however, style is never compromised with elegant designs and high-quality finishes our king-size mattresses for back pain serve both functional and aesthetic appeal.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy choose Damro's king-size mattress\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;Damro is a furniture brand known for providing high-quality furniture options for several years.\u0026nbsp; With extensive designs and innovative solutions for your home, we provide the best functional and durable furniture at affordable pricing.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSuperior craftsmanship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEach mattress has exceptional craftsmanship. Using high-grade materials expert craftsmen design and manufacture exquisite styles and finishes. With functional features and aesthetically pleasing \u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/lcmd78724-dura-coir-mattress-maroon-2492-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eking-size mattresses under 20000\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e from Damro to adorn your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCustomer satisfaction\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur king-size mattress doesn’t just offer support, it is made from breathable fabrics to ensure a cooler environment. Healthwise the mattress also has\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003ehypoallergenic properties promoting healthier sleeping space. The mattress with so many features within your budget makes it the perfect buy.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eShop with us\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePick the perfect mattresses from our online collection or showroom for king-size mattresses near you\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eto experience the high standards of quality and comfort from Damro. We help you pick the ideal mattress ensuring you have a seamless shopping experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","metaDescription":"Save without compromising comfort with king size mattresses offered at great value. Explore affordable king size mattress options and shop online today.","metaKeywords":"king size mattress, memory foam king mattress, coir king mattress, spring king mattress, large mattress, Damro mattresses","metaTitle":"Buy Affordable King Size Mattresses Online with high Build Quality ","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"King Size Mattresses | Memory Foam, Coir \u0026 Spring | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/king-size-mattresses\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s range of king size mattresses including memory foam, coir, and spring types. Designed for maximum comfort, support, and durability.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eSuperior Comfort with King size mattresses from Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","homeCategoryImg":"","offer":null,"regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f4d60c31970","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7fb0a0c31971","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f696bc31972","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f3a6dc31973","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f8938c31974","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7fc60cc31975","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f761ec31976","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f7633c31977","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f777ac31978","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7fe5e6c31979","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7fed14c3197a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f5becc3197b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f3eadc3197c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7fd368c3197d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25b6a54b7f11ccc3197e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}]},{"_id":"60b61874a4604b0430f2bbda","name":"Single Mattresses","description":"Create a restful sleep haven with Damro’s Single Mattresses. Choose from memory foam for pressure relief, coir for natural support, or traditional spring for bounce and resilience. Compact yet supportive, these mattresses are ideal for children’s rooms, guest beds, and smaller spaces—delivering comfort and quality night after night.\n\n","image":"","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b6180ba4604b0430f2bbd7","ourcollection":false,"icon":"","categoryImage":"","sortValue":2,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T06:23:37.305Z","__v":0,"slug":"single-mattresses","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eExperience Unmatched Comfort and Quality with Our Single Mattresses\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eA single mattress is an important ingredient for a person who wants the right combination of utility and comfort. A single mattress for the home can make a world of difference, whether you are decorating a child's bedroom, setting up a guestroom, or changing your own sleeping arrangements. Bring to Damro's extensive inventory high-quality mattresses to cater to every demand and taste.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eWhy Single Mattresses for Your Home\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eThese compact mattresses perfectly fit very small spaces and have made them probably the best choice for smaller bedrooms, studio apartments, and even shared homes. Give excellent support and total comfort for an individual sleeper. Damro understands how important it is for anyone to sleep a good night; therefore, not even the lightweight mattresses for single beds from our collection is deprived of the superior comfort and durability trait it possesses.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eFeatures of the Best Single Mattresses for Comfort\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen selecting a single mattress, comfort should be your top priority. Here are some features that make our mattresses stand out:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eErgonomic Design: The best single mattresses for comfort are crafted to support the natural curvature of your spine, ensuring proper alignment and reducing pressure points, and single mattresses for kids.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eHigh-Quality Materials: From memory foam to pocket springs, our mattresses are made using premium materials that enhance comfort and durability.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eBreathable Fabrics: Our comfortable foam single mattresses feature breathable fabrics that regulate temperature and keep you cool throughout the night.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAnti-Allergy Protection: Many of our mattresses come with hypoallergenic properties, making them a safe choice for individuals with allergies or sensitivities and Orthopaedic single mattresses are also available.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eBenefits of choosing Damro's mattresses\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eInnovative technology, quality, and affordability motivate Damro to manufacture the best single mattresses for comfort. So here are the reasons loved and preferred by customers for our single mattresses:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eCustomizable Options: Firm by way of back support or just so you can snuggle with it, every available option is here to match your need.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eDurability: Our mattresses are built for longevity, making them a smart investment that offers great bang for the buck in the long run.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eEco-friendly Materials: We believe in sustainability and use a lot of our products with eco-friendly materials.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCheap Pricing: Premium features do not mean premium prices. Affordable single-size mattresses are willing to offer luxurious features at pocket-friendly rates. Our price starts from\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eTips for Choosing the Perfect Single Mattress for Home\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eConsider the Size: Measure your bed frame to ensure the mattress fits perfectly.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAssess Comfort Needs: Test different firmness levels to find the one that suits you best.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eLook for Added Features: Features like motion isolation and edge support can enhance your sleeping experience.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSet a Budget: Determine how much you’re willing to spend without compromising on quality.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eConclusion\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eInvesting in a high-quality single mattress for the home is essential for ensuring a good night's sleep. At Damro, we take pride in offering the best single mattresses for comfort, combining superior craftsmanship with innovative features. Explore our collection today and discover the perfect mattress to meet your needs. With Damro, you can rest assured that your comfort is our priority.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","metaDescription":"Discover durable single mattresses designed for back support. Shop single bed foam mattress varieties and best single bed mattress picks online today.","metaKeywords":"single mattress, memory foam single mattress, coir mattress single, spring mattress single, kids mattress, Damro mattresses","metaTitle":"Buy Single Mattresses with Foam Comfort \u0026 Strong Back Support","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Single Mattresses – Coir, Foam \u0026 Spring | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/single-mattresses\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s single mattress collection, featuring coir, memory foam, and spring mattresses that provide comfort and support for kids’ rooms, guest bedrooms, and compact spaces.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover the Most Comfortable Single Mattress at Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null,"regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7f93b5c31980","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7ffc2cc31981","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7f01c4c31982","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7f5038c31983","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7f313bc31984","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7f2beec31985","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7fab92c31986","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7fd1bfc31987","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7f6c32c31988","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7fdc2ac31989","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7f69d0c3198a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7fac70c3198b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7fedb8c3198c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7fd1efc3198d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da25e9a54b7f402ac3198e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}]}]}]},{"_id":"60b5dae8a4604b0430f2bba1","name":"Dining Sets","slug":"dining-sets","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Dining Table Sets - 4, 6 \u0026 8 Seater | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/dining-sets\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s wide range of dining sets including 4-seater, 6-seater, and 8-seater options. Designed for comfort and elegance, ideal for modern Indian homes.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e","sortValue":4,"description":"Create memorable dining experiences with Damro’s stylish and functional Dining Sets. Available in 4‑, 6‑, and 8‑seater options, each set combines elegant materials like solid wood, glass, and metal. Perfectly paired with coordinating dining chairs and designed for both everyday use and special gatherings, these sets are built to last and uplift your dining space.","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/8 Dining Table.jpg","subcategory":[{"_id":"60b618efa4604b0430f2bbdc","name":"Dining Table Sets","slug":"dining-table-sets","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/35.jpg","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/8 Dining Table.jpg","description":"Create a welcoming dining space with Damro’s Dining Table Sets. Available in 4‑, 6‑, and 8‑seater configurations, these sets feature stylish materials like solid wood, tempered glass, and quality metal detailing. Complement with matching chairs and pair with our dining storage ranges for a cohesive décor feel.","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Dining Table Sets – 4, 6 \u0026 8 Seater | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/dining-table-sets\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s dining table sets online, available in multiple sizes and elegant designs. Perfect for small families, large gatherings, and stylish dining rooms.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"60b61939a4604b0430f2bbde","name":"4 Seater Dining Table Sets","description":"Explore Damro's premium collection of 4-seater dining table sets, meticulously designed to enhance your dining space. Elevate your dining experience with our exquisite range of furniture that seamlessly combines style, comfort, and functionality. Crafted with precision, our 4-seater dining sets offer a perfect blend of aesthetics and durability, adding a touch of elegance to your home. Choose from a variety of contemporary and traditional designs, each thoughtfully created to cater to your unique taste. With Damro, you're not just getting furniture – you're investing in long-lasting quality and timeless appeal. Create cherished moments around our 4-seater dining table sets, the heart of your home's gatherings. Redefine your dining area today with Damro's signature craftsmanship\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/34.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b618efa4604b0430f2bbdc","ourcollection":false,"icon":"","categoryImage":"","sortValue":1,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T07:10:58.895Z","__v":0,"slug":"4-seater-dining-table-sets","enable":true,"metaDescription":"Find value with 4 seater dining table set arrangements that suit everyday use. From dining table set 4 seater wooden to modern finishes, get thoughtful designs.","metaKeywords":"4-seater dining table, Dining table sets, Small dining table, Round dining table, Modern dining set, Wooden dining table, Compact dining furniture, Space-saving dining, Contemporary dining set, Kitchen table and chairs","metaTitle":"Buy 4 Seater Dining Table Set Online with new designs upto 40% off","seoMarkup":"\"\u003cscript type=\"\"application/ld+json\"\"\u003e\n{\n  \"\"@context\"\": \"\"https://schema.org/\"\",\n  \"\"@type\"\": \"\"WebSite\"\",\n  \"\"name\"\": \"\"Damro Furniture\"\",\n  \"\"url\"\": \"\"https://damroindia.com/\"\",\n  \"\"potentialAction\"\": {\n    \"\"@type\"\": \"\"SearchAction\"\",\n    \"\"target\"\": \"\"https://damroindia.com/4-seater-dining-table-sets{search_term_string}\"\",\n    \"\"query-input\"\": \"\"required name=search_term_string\"\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\"\n","bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eBring Home A Perfect 4 Seater Dining Table\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eA perfect dining space can become special when all your loved ones are together at meal times. Owning a comfortable and spacious \u003cstrong\u003efour-seater dining table\u003c/strong\u003e ensures enjoyable and intimate gatherings. From coffee to brunches with casual conversations on an elegant dining table set, it can redefine your dining experience.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSeveral 4-seater dining tables online sites\u003cstrong\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003emay not provide the same quality and finish that Damro’s dining sets provide with their impressive collection. Picking an ideal dining table with our contemporary aesthetics, traditional wooden designs and a blend of both in a marble or glass top setting enhances your dining space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhy choose Damro’s 4-seater dining table set\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpace-saving set:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eDamro’s 4-seater dining set offers an elegant furniture piece to adorn your dining space fitting perfectly in compact and medium layouts.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDesign versatility:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eNot just regular dining sets, but 4-seater dining tables that scream style and elegance. From sleek wooden tables to marble and glass tops to match your preferences suiting your home décor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDurable materials:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003ePremium fabric for your 4-seater dining upholstery is available in a variety of colours and patterns. High-end craftsmanship using solid, engineered wood and tempered glass sourced with quality checks make Damro’s 4-seater dining table durable.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eComfortable seating:\u003c/strong\u003e A wooden 4-seater dining table set offers a relaxed dining experience. The padded and upholstered seating is ergonomically designed to provide ample comfort during meal times and other occasions.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEasy maintenance:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eThe use of tempered glass and scratch-resistant finishes surface of Damro’s 4 seater dining set assures of long-lasting appeal. Smooth surfaces prevent spills and stains from staying on, making them easier to clean and maintain.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eVarious 4-seater dining tables at Damro\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStonic 4 seater dining table set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eTake home a durable and stylish \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/stonic-4-seater-dining-table-set-86698670-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eStonic 4 seater dining table set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e with a sturdy teak wood base to create memorable moments. The dining table comes with a 12-month warranty period and EMI options making it easy to purchase while adding a touch of elegance to your dining space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVision 4 seater dining table set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA budget-friendly \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/wdvn001-wooden-dining-vision-suite-nar05cherry-11963-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVision 4 seater dining table set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e for compact homes has a wooden structure, veneer top and seats upholstered with premium fabric. Buying Damro’s 4 seater dining table set has a 12-month warranty and comes with a matt lacquered finish to match your décor.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCanton 4 seater dining table set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBring the elegant \u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/canton-4-seater-dining-set-531212169-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCanton 4 seater dining table set\u003c/strong\u003e \u003c/a\u003ewith a lacquered finish to host your guests. This solid wood dining table set has cushioned seats with diamond-designed detailing. With an assurance of a 12-month warranty, you can take home a durable and lasting 4-seater dining table set to enjoy all your meals.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMittal 4 seater dining table set\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/mittal-4-seater-dining-set-27612759-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMittal 4 seater dining table set \u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003ea competitively priced and elegant round dining table set with four chairs can be purchased from Damro. The ergonomically designed chairs and sturdy structure of the 4 seater dining table are made from Sheesham wood. Being space efficient in terms of shape and design provides great functionality and relaxation.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eExplore Stylish 4 Seater Dining Table Designs for Every Home\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184982800e7b7a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b1849365f0e7b7b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184962820e7b7c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b18494c1e0e7b7d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b18490e0d0e7b7e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b1849770a0e7b7f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184927c60e7b80","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184920070e7b81","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184952b80e7b82","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184908560e7b83","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184930c30e7b84","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184913240e7b85","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b18499dbf0e7b86","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b184927000e7b87","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da31028b18498cfa0e7b88","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"60b6194ea4604b0430f2bbdf","name":"6 Seater Dining Table Sets","description":"Discover the epitome of dining luxury with DAMRO's exclusive collection of 6-seater dining table sets. Elevate your dining space with our meticulously crafted designs that seamlessly blend style and comfort. Our 6-seater sets create the perfect ambiance for shared moments, combining spaciousness and sophistication. Choose from an array of contemporary and timeless options, each showcasing DAMRO's commitment to quality craftsmanship. Elevate your family gatherings and dinner parties with the allure of our 6-seater dining table sets, a harmonious fusion of aesthetics and functionality. Redefine your dining area today with DAMRO's signature elegance and durability, where every meal becomes an exquisite experience","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/35.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b618efa4604b0430f2bbdc","ourcollection":true,"icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Dinning.png","categoryImage":"","sortValue":2,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T07:21:07.542Z","__v":0,"slug":"6-seater-dining-table-sets","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eA dining space is not just where food is consumed, you partake in the joy of sharing interesting stories and creating memories all happening over a meal. So, when you want a dining table 6 seater size wherein you would share the table with friends and family, you need it to be special and accommodating. Damro’s 6-seater dining table set is a perfect combination of functionality and design to complete your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe appeal of 6-seater dining table sets\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSpacious and comfortable\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhen you have a large family or a big group of friends for a meal, there needs to be a proper seating arrangement to enjoy the meal comfortably. A modern dining table set 6 seater will ensure all your guests can sit back and relax while tucking into scrumptious food. Damro’s design of a 6 seater dining table has enough room for everyone to dine comfortably.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFits any layout\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhether your dining space is compact or large, Damro’s dining tables can fit into any décor. A\u0026nbsp; 6 seater dining table with chairs can fit into an open-plan living area or dedicated dining room. With different shapes to choose from including circular, rectangle, oval, and others to suit different layouts and preferences.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRelaxed dining experience\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eA well-designed dining table can ensure you have a relaxed dining experience. The chairs are well-crafted and sturdy for regular usage. Ergonomics is employed to ensure comfortable seating and excellent support. The tables provide enough space for each member to sit and enough space to move around as well.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAmazing\u0026nbsp; aesthetics\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEach dining table is made from high-quality materials including wood, glass top, marble, etc. Crafted using the latest technology to provide the perfect designs on solid wood or tempered glass. Damro’s dining table 6 seater latest designs sets have premium finishes adding to their aesthetic appeal. You could choose the rustic wooden finish or ask for the modern sleek look for style.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTop picks from Damro’s dining table collection\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/henry-6-seater-dining-set-61476144-Bengaluru\"\u003eHenry 6 Seater Dining Set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/jacob-6-seater-dining-set-61486145-Bengaluru\"\u003eJacob 6 Seater Dining Set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/cooper-6-seater-dining-set-275727512748-Bengaluru\"\u003eCooper 6 Seater Dining Set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/milani-6-seater-dining-set-55535548-Bengaluru\"\u003eMilani 6 Seater Dining Set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/lucas-6-seater-dining-set-61496146-Bengaluru\"\u003eLucas 6 Seater Dining Set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCare and maintenance of 6 seater dining table sets\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eTo retain the quality and lifespan of the \u003cstrong\u003e6 seater dining table sets\u003c/strong\u003e, here are some tips to follow\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eCleaning regularly will ensure that dust accumulation and staining do not spoil the surface of the dining table. Wipe using a soft damp cloth to clear up after meals can help keep the dining table in pristine condition.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAvoid heat and moisture to come in contact with the surface of the table. Even direct heat sources near the table are not a good idea.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCheck and tighten screws and bolts, once in a while and ensure they are tight and secure.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eConclusion\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBuying a 6 seater dining table set can make a difference to your home, you can now have an enjoyable experience hosting dinner parties for family and friends. Space and seating in the dining room are taken care of by Damro’s vast collection of dining table sets. Style comfort and functionality are part of the appeal of 6 seater dining table sets.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","metaDescription":"Explore 6 seater dining table sets crafted with premium wood finishes. Choose designs from the modern dining table set.","metaKeywords":"6 Seater Dining Table Sets, 6-seater dining table, Dining table sets, Large dining table, Rectangular dining table, Modern dining set, Wooden dining table Spacious dining furniture, Family dining set, Contemporary dining table, Stylish dining room sets","metaTitle":"Buy 6 Seater Dining Table Sets with Wood Finishes upto 35% off","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebSite\",\n  \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n  \"url\": \"https://damroindia.com/\",\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://damroindia.com/6-seater-dining-table-sets{search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover the appeal of Damro’s 6 seater dining table sets\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Category Page opt 2 - Dining.jpg","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f1fd5c319f1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Dinning.png","hoverIcon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Dinning.png","image":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Dinning.png","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Category Page opt 2 - Dining.jpg","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f8630c319f2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7fba3ac319f3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f353ec319f4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7fbb72c319f5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f5230c319f6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f4969c319f7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f950cc319f8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f6dc9c319f9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f7885c319fa","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f86d3c319fb","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f52d8c319fc","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f4401c319fd","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f2bc3c319fe","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3363a54b7f08dbc319ff","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"60b6195ea4604b0430f2bbe0","name":"8 Seater Dining Table Sets","description":"Host memorable dinner events with Damro’s 8‑Seater Dining Table Sets. Crafted from premium materials like solid wood, tempered glass, and durable upholstery, these sets deliver both elegance and practicality—ideal for enhancing your dining space and accommodating guests in style.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/36.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b618efa4604b0430f2bbdc","ourcollection":false,"icon":"","categoryImage":"","sortValue":3,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T07:28:00.392Z","__v":0,"slug":"8-seater-dining-table-sets","enable":true,"metaDescription":"Shop 8 seater dining table sets built for comfort and durability. Find family-friendly designs and order your 8 seater dining table set online ","metaKeywords":"8 seater dining table, 8 seater dining set, large dining table, family dining sets, Damro dining tables","metaTitle":"Buy 8 Seater Dining Table Sets online and get upto 40% off","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"8‑Seater Dining Table Sets – Elegant \u0026 Spacious | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/8-seater-dining-table-sets\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s collection of 8‑seater dining table sets designed for large families and gatherings. Featuring wood, glass, and upholstered options with robust design.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","bottomContent":"\u003cp\u003eHosting a large family or a group of friends at home may seem a hassle. However, \u0026nbsp;an \u003cstrong\u003e8-seater dining table\u003c/strong\u003e can transform your dining room into an inviting and spacious space, making any celebration a hit. With confidence and pride, place food and seat your guests comfortably with Damro’s dining table sets ensuring every gathering becomes special. Bring home the perfect table to enjoy meals in a blend of comfort and elegance while adding to the décor of your dining space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eChoosing from the wide array of \u003cstrong\u003e8-seater dining options online\u003c/strong\u003e, Damro’s affordable and aesthetically pleasing designs can inspire memorable mealtime conversations. You can pick the latest collection of wooden designs, marble tops and glass top options for your dining room. Buying a dining table can make any meal enjoyable allowing the gathering of all loved ones at a designated place.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhy pick an 8-seater dining table set?\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHosting family \u0026amp; friends:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eLarge families and friends can enjoy comfortable meal times with a spacious dining table set.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMulti-functional design:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eWorks well as a workspace, study area and even a great spot for creative activities like board games when not used for meals.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eOptimized space usage:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eA \u003cstrong\u003edining table set 8 seater size\u003c/strong\u003e has a space-saving innovative design suiting both medium and large dining areas also with optimized framework.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDiverse styles:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eApart from traditional wooden dining table sets, you can opt for marble or glass tops from our \u003cstrong\u003emodern dining table set 8-seater collection\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVaried shape choices:\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003eNo matter the layout of your dining area, Damro’s 8-seater dining set has all spaces to offer from rectangular to square. Those who don’t like corners can opt for round and oval shapes to meet your requirements.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3\u003eDamro’s 8-seater dining table set collection\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h4\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/willow-8-seater-dining-set-80008001-Bengaluru\"\u003eWillow 8-seater dining table set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe dining set of 8 has upholstered seats and is made of a solid wood structure. A lacquered finish adds to the elegance and modern touch. The 8-seater dining table has a warranty of 12 months, an EMI option and shipment within 5 days can become a good investment for your home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/nevada-8-seater-dining-set-81915447-Bengaluru\"\u003eNevada 8-seater dining table set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eAn 8-seater dining table with chairs upholstered with premium fabric and solid wood structure. A matte lacquered finish brings a contemporary feel to the set. The ergonomic design and style of the eight chairs ensure comfort and elegance. A 12-month warranty and EMI option on Damro’s 8-seater dining set to make your dining space stand out\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/veloster-8-seater-dining-set-86678668-Bengaluru\"\u003eVeloster 8-seater dining table set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eEntertain your family and friends on this centerpiece of your dining area. Unmatchable craftsmanship has engineered the marble top to the robust teak wood structure to make a lasting impression on the diners. This easy-to-maintain and durable product has a 12-month warranty and an EMI option from Damro’s 8-seater dining table set.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://www.damroindia.com/tency-8-seater-dining-table-set-27642754-Bengaluru\"\u003eTency 8-seater dining table set\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eTransforming your dining area with an 8-seater dining table made from Sheesham wood. This handcrafted dining table has upholstered chairs made from premium fabric with wood wood-stained lacquer finish to match the elegance of your space. Purchasing an 8 seater dining table set can become a good investment as it not only matches style but comes with a warranty and EMI option.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eUpgrade Your Dining Space with Stunning 8 Seater Table Sets\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849301e0e7b9a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849a8060e7b9b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849fd4c0e7b9c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b18492a430e7b9d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849ef060e7b9e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b18494afa0e7b9f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b18491c800e7ba0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b18490d770e7ba1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849c4f10e7ba2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849853a0e7ba3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849542b0e7ba4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b184926010e7ba5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849e2870e7ba6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b1849052a0e7ba7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da35008b184900910e7ba8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null}]},{"_id":"60b6198aa4604b0430f2bbe1","name":"Dining Storage","slug":"dining-storage","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/37.jpg","icon":"","description":"Organize your dining essentials with Damro’s Tableware \u0026 Dining Storage collection. From beautifully crafted crockery units and buffet cabinets to sleek sideboards and display racks, our furniture combines style with functionality—perfect for showcasing dinnerware, storing glassware, and adding matching décor to your dining space.","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Dining Storage Units – Cabinets \u0026 Sideboards | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/dining-storage\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s range of dining storage furniture including sideboards, cabinets, and more. Perfect for organizing crockery, cutlery, and dining essentials in style.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"60b619cda4604b0430f2bbe2","name":"Crockery Units and Dining Cabinets","description":"Upgrade your dining area with Damro’s range of crockery units and dining cabinets. Designed for both style and functionality, these storage solutions offer ample space for your dinnerware, glasses, and kitchen essentials, creating a neat and inviting dining environment.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/36.jpg","menuImage":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/36.jpg","level":2,"parentId":"60b6198aa4604b0430f2bbe1","ourcollection":false,"icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/37.jpg","categoryImage":"","sortValue":0,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-07-07T11:20:39.506Z","__v":0,"slug":"crockery-unit-and-dining-cabinets","enable":true,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eShop Beautifully Designed Crockery Units and Cabinets for Every Home\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eValuable items must be taken care of. In order to preserve their beauty and sentimental value, Damro provides an exquisite range of crockery units. These storage solutions are designed to keep your crockery clean, secure, and well-organized for years to come.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCrockery Cabinets: The Perfect Blend of Style and Functionality\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro's crockery cabinets and stands have shelves and drawers designed to carry all your crockery items comfortably. From plates and bowls to fine glassware, these cabinets dedicate a separate place for every single item, which will never be damaged or scratched. The ample shelf space accommodates easy stacking, while the drawers can be used to store loose items or other smaller items.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eNot only are these units functional but also add to the beauty of your home. A designed crockery cabinet lets you show off some of your treasured pieces, elevating the sophistication and charm within your dining space or living space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eWhy Choose a Damro Crockery Unit?\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eProtect Your Crockery\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eAvoid mishaps and damage by storing your delicate crockery in a secure cabinet. With multiple shelves and drawers, Damro’s units ensure your collection remains safe and organized.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eOptimize Space\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eAre you struggling with limited kitchen space? No worries.\u0026nbsp; Our well-crockery cabinet helps declutter your kitchen and dining area by providing a systematic way to store your crockery. It also takes full advantage of available space and keeps everything within easy reach.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eKeep Crockery Dust-Free\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eLeaving crockery exposed to dust can lead to gradual wear and tear. Damro’s cabinets protect your pieces from dust and grime, ensuring they stay clean and well-maintained over time.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eElevate your Experience with Damro\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAdd an extra touch to your dining by using Damro's stylish and functional crockery units. Look through our collection today to find the perfect solution for protecting your collection while beautifying your interior.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat to Consider Before Buying a Crockery Unit\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAt Damro, our crockery unit range is designed to come in a wide variety of styles and types to fit any room. Choosing the right unit for your home can be pretty confusing, but if you consider a few things, it becomes easy and simple.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e1. Budget\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSetting a budget before one goes shopping is very important. It provides an opportunity to find options that fall within your price range and not overspend. Here at Damro, we have crockery units in various price ranges: 13,000 to 32,000 Rs, thereby letting you find the right product that fits within your budget.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e2. Available of Space\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAssess the available space in your dining or kitchen area before you make a purchase for a crockery unit. Ensure that the unit is placed comfortably and not overcrowding the room. For a doored crockery unit, allow for additional space to be taken up by the opening of the doors. Damro has different designs that can range from compact to large-sized units, according to your needs and size of the room.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e3. Storage Needs\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe most essential factor in determining a crockery unit is an understanding of one's storage requirements. If someone requires a considerable amount of space for dinnerware and utensil organization, multiple shelves and drawers can be chosen for that purpose. Damro's crockery units balance functionality with great style, ensuring it can suit any purpose.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eExplore Crockery Units at Damro\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro’s stylish and practical crockery units are designed to enhance your dining experience. Whether you’re prioritizing storage, display, or both, you’ll find a wide selection to choose from. Visit Damro stores or browse online to discover high-quality furniture for your kitchen, dining area, and home.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBring home a crockery unit that perfectly complements your interiors!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","hoverIcon":"","metaDescription":"Explore our Crockery Units and Dining Cabinets. Our compact wooden chest of drawers greatly fits your bedroom, living room even your kids' room. Order today. \n","metaKeywords":"crockery units, dining cabinets, crockery cabinets, dining storage, kitchen storage furniture, Damro dining storage","metaTitle":"Buy Dining Crockery Cabinet Units online in India | Damro","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Crockery Units \u0026 Dining Cabinets | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/crockery-unit-and-dining-cabinets\",\n  \"description\": \"Discover Damro’s premium crockery units and dining cabinets. Crafted with quality and elegance to provide practical storage and enhance your dining area decor.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eUpgrade Your Dining Space with Elegant Crockery Units from Damro\u003c/h2\u003e","lastUpdatedBy":"67922c2b9420091d5a35492c","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/36.jpg","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a5553949a93961a5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/crock.jpg","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a5553946ff3961a6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a555390fe13961a7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a55539357c3961a8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a55539386c3961a9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a55539314e3961aa","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a55539addd3961ab","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a5553966f03961ac","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a555390c773961ad","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a55539558d3961ae","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a55539f92d3961af","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a555393d083961b0","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a555395b513961b1","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a5553952423961b2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"686bad87a555394e8f3961b3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null}]}]},{"_id":"60b5dafba4604b0430f2bba2","name":"Study and Office Furniture","slug":"study-office-furniture","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Study \u0026 Office Furniture – Desks, Chairs \u0026 Storage | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/study-office-furniture\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s study and office furniture collection featuring desks, chairs, shelves, and storage units tailored for home offices, study rooms, and professional workspaces.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","sortValue":5,"description":"Study and Office Furniture\nExcellent store with premium quality furniture range. Damro product is known for its quality and durability. We are regular customer and have purchased many products from Damro in the past.(Sofa, upholstery, chairs, wall mounts etc). The service is excellent and after sales services are also great. The staff is courteous and always available to help","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Table.jpg","subcategory":[{"_id":"60b61aada4604b0430f2bbe5","name":"Tables","slug":"tables","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/39.jpg","icon":"","description":"Explore Damro’s diverse table offerings designed to suit every room and purpose. From elegant dining tables and cozy center/coffee tables to ergonomic study/computer desks and professional office tables, each piece combines functional design, quality materials, and timeless aesthetics. Perfect for enhancing your home, office, or study area.\n\n","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Tables – Dining, Study \u0026 Center Tables | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/tables\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s collection of versatile tables including dining tables, study desks, coffee tables, and center tables designed for style and functionality in all rooms.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"60b61f0ba4604b0430f2bbfb","name":"Study and Computer Tables","description":"Enhance productivity with Damro’s Study \u0026 Computer Tables collection. Featuring sturdy designs, spacious work surfaces, and convenient storage like shelves and drawers, our tables are perfect for students and professionals alike. Designed for comfort and durability, they blend seamlessly into study spaces and home offices.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/38.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61aada4604b0430f2bbe5","ourcollection":true,"icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/11 Study.jpg","categoryImage":"","sortValue":0,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T07:56:29.575Z","__v":0,"slug":"study-tables-and-computer-tables","enable":true,"metaDescription":"Get high-utility computer study tables online. Choose models with storage, drawers, or wheels to suit your workspace with long-lasting build and comfort.","metaKeywords":"study tables, computer tables, student desk, home office desk, ergonomic study table, Damro desks","metaTitle":"Buy Computer Study Tables with Storage \u0026 Drawer Options","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Study \u0026 Computer Tables – Functional Desks | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/study-tables-and-computer-tables\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s collection of study tables and computer desks, ideal for students, home offices and workspaces. Offering ergonomic design, smart storage, and modern style.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eBuy Modern Study and Computer Tables for Every Space\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eA well-designed study or computer table can significantly enhance productivity and organization, making it an essential piece of furniture for homes, offices, or study spaces. At Damro, we offer a versatile range of Study tables for home and Computer tables for work from home that blend style, durability, and functionality. Whether you need a simple workstation or a multipurpose desk, our collection has something for everyone. This guide will help you decide when choosing your ideal table.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThings before buying a study table or computer table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003ePurpose and Use: Understand your reason for using the table before deciding on one. Will it be for Study tables for home, Computer tables for work-from-home, or both? Knowing the purpose helps you choose the appropriate size, storage types, and additional options.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eRoom Size and Layout: Take room dimensions before you start choosing the table, even considering that the table can fit where you will place it without it overcrowding the space. Measure the furniture other than the table and make way for people to walk around it.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eErgonomics: Choose a healthy posture-promoting table. With height and ergonomic level adjustment, you will be able to avoid any strain when working and studying for hours on end.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eStorage Space: Think of what you need to store. Are drawers, shelves, or compartments necessary for organizing the books, files, and accessories? You can purchase the table based on your needs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBudget: Make a budget because it will narrow your choices and give you options. Damro have tables in many price ranges starting from 3000 to 15,000 INR and making it easy for you to find one that fits your budget.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eConsiderations before purchase\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eMaterial and Longevity: A table's makeup denotes its longevity and semblance. Damro tables are constructed of the finest quality materials, such as engineered wood, solid wood, and metal, for more durability and style.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSize and Measurements: Choose Table Size That Best Fits in the Space Available and Its Requirements. A small room can employ compact designs, while an extra-large table with that extra storage works for a larger area.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDesign and Style: Your laptop-friendly study tables or computer tables have to flow smoothly into your interior décor. Modern study table designs with minimalistic to classic wood finishes and everything in between, Damro has it covered for you.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eStorage Facility and Organization: Considerations could cover cable management systems, dedicated keyboard trays, or built-in storage. These eventually render more convenience and help keep your workspace really tidy.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAssembly and Maintenance: It should also be easy to assemble and maintain the table. Damro's tables will be ready for you to set up with almost no maintenance.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eWhat Are the Options Available at Damro\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro offers an extensive range of study and Compact computer tables:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eBasic Study Tables: Compact and functional designs ideal for students or minimalist spaces.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eComputer Desks: Equipped with features like keyboard trays, cable management, and monitor stands for efficient workspace organization.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMultipurpose Workstations: Combine storage and workspace, offering drawers, shelves, and cabinets for enhanced utility.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eWhy Choose Damro Study and Computer Tables?\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eFlawless Craftsmanship: Damro is India's premier brand in high-quality furniture. All the study and computer tables are constructed with the finest materials, thus offering beautiful finishes and long life.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eThoughtful Space Usage: The Computer desk for small spaces is perfect with the right features, from storage space to ergonomic study tables, assembled from very detailed ideas to suit the needs of the user.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAffordable study desks:\u0026nbsp;Damro becomes quality at price when a huge collection can be made available easily to everyone while ensuring seasonal ingenuity and special offers for more cost-cutting solutions.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eShop the Best Study and Computer Tables for Work and Study\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/ksd024-study-desk-with-storage-drawer-m42m51-7035-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eDaisy Study Table With Side Storage\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/ksd003-study-desk-with-cupboard--drawers-m42-6227-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMizzen Study Table With Drawer \u0026amp; Shutter\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/ksd008-study-desk-with-adjustable-top-m42-6228-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIntelli Study Table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/ksd019-study-desk-with-2-door--adjustable-top-m42m41-7155-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eCarrel Study Table with Drawer \u0026amp; Cupboard\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kct034-computer-table-with-castors-m42-9231-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAero Computer Table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/bkct002-computer-table-m02-10218-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eSwift Computer Table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/ksd020-study-desk-with-2-door--adjustable-top-m42m41-9647-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eManiac Study Table with Drawer \u0026amp; Cupboard\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/ksd025-study-desk-with-drawer--cupboard-m42m41-10046-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMilli Study Table with Drawer \u0026amp; Cupboard\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/ksd026-study-desk-with-drawer--cupboard-m11m27-10412-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTampa Study Table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eEnhance your workspace with Damro’s study and computer tables\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA functional and stylish study or computer table is a valuable investment in productivity and organization. Damro’s extensive collection caters to every need, whether it’s for a dedicated home office, a student’s study corner, or a versatile workstation. With Ergonomic Study tables with storage design, durable materials, and customizable options, you can find the perfect table to complement your space.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eChoose Damro for high-quality furniture that combines practicality with elegance. Explore our range of study and computer tables today and transform your workspace into an efficient and inspiring environment.\u003c/p\u003e","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eDiscover the Perfect Study and Computer Tables for Your Needs\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f5484c31a01","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/11 Study.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/38.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f8c16c31a02","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be944857d10564675e9edf"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f0fc2c31a03","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5d07cfcaa12dcc5e58a1"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f38a1c31a04","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c5a67cfcaa16cb95e5875"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f7b00c31a05","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a1579dcfcaa1ecd95e5a0f"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f3d7bc31a06","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"67ca79edf887836e240b9696","offer":""},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f2237c31a07","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f72fcc31a08","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7fd397c31a09","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7fb1eec31a0a","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7feab2c31a0b","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7fbdb2c31a0c","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f48cbc31a0d","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f15d2c31a0e","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a"},{"ourcollection":false,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3bada54b7f3cbdc31a0f","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","image":"","homeCategoryImg":"","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f"}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"6299fe0e72f0e674db4edcc1","ourcollection":true,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Office Tables","description":"Enhance productivity with Damro’s Office Tables range. Featuring ergonomic workstations, spacious study desks, and elegant executive tables, each piece is thoughtfully designed for durability and comfort—perfect for home offices, corporate settings, and focused workspaces.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/39.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61aada4604b0430f2bbe5","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Table.jpg","slug":"office-tables","sortValue":1,"metaTitle":"Buy wooden Office Tables with Modern Design @ 40 % off","metaDescription":"Find office tables online designed for work efficiency. Options include executive office tables, wooden office tables, and modern office tables.","metaKeywords":"office tables, work desks, study tables, computer desks, executive tables, office workstation, Damro office furniture","createdAt":"2022-06-03T12:26:54.174Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T07:58:21.937Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eElevate Your Productivity with Damro’s Office Tables\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe office table is probably the most important part of any workspace. Be it a home office or the new addition of a corporate environment, they are as crucial as important to the workspace when choosing the best office tables for workspaces. This changes everything: comfort, productivity, and aesthetics. We have different models and office tables that suit each office need at Damro, as we understand how modernizing works with diverse needs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eSignificance of Office Tables in Workspaces\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eOffice tables form a major part of any workspace. They serve not only as mere functional furniture but also create the entire ambiance. A well-designed office table would boost efficiency, promote better posture, and better organize work essentials, whereas an ill-designed office table can do just the opposite by hindering productivity and introducing discomfort. Office desks for productivity are the best investments you can make in employee well-being and business success.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eFactors to consider before buying Office Tables\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe need for an ideal office table is generally based on a few considerations that help one realize the needs as far as the workspace is concerned:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePurpose and Functionality: A different function requires a different workstation. Some may include a large work surface, storage, and other amenities usually for executive desks; those for minimalist workstations are made for keeping everything inside. Determine the kinds of activities to be held and choose a table appropriate for the activities.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eErgonomics: The parameter of comfort is started with productivity. Therefore, available ergonomic office tables align the posture of users and ensure lesser strain and fatigue. Such include height-adjustable height office desks, while some fit well with ergonomic chairs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eMaterial and Build Quality: The factor in the longevity of office tables is essential for their intended long-term use. Implementation of solid wood, metals, or engineered materials is in favor of long-lasting strong options that fit your style preference and budget.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eBeauty: Beauty is in the showcase department of office tables. The usual sleek and Modular office desks will perfectly fit a contemporary office, while a conventional wooden table will suit a more traditional ambiance.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eSpace Optimization: This is for offices with smaller space-saving office desks, and for the shared workspace, it can accommodate compact office desks with built-in storage. Larger offices may have sprawling executive tables or collaborative kind of workstations.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eDamro Office Tables for Your Workplace\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro guarantees versatility concerning the requirement for office tables; as far as office preference goes, we have it all. Highlights from the collection are discussed as follows:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eExecutive Desks\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eWith a bit of guidance from you, executive desks, created for CEOs, combine taste with utility. Wonderfully spacious, with integrated storage and a beautiful and proud appearance, these tables create an aura of seriousness.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eWorkstations\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor open offices, our modular workstation promotes cooperation and, at the same time, comfort for each individual. Modular workstations are made for the compatible distribution of office layouts.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eHome Office Tables\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eOur home office tables are also just perfect. Work from home has suitably blended the best of both worlds- comfort and efficiency. Space using compact yet functional tables within the home makes effective corners for one's workspace.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eHeight-Adjustable Desks\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eAn overall great adjustable height office desk with the sitting or standing workspace option would fit the job perfect with such people. These desks offer a healthy method to keep a focus at work.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eCollaborative Tables\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003eEncourages team spirit and cooperation on different surfaces, with many ways to create brainstorming interpretations, keeping a separate area to cater for meetings and brainstorming sessions.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhy Damro?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDamro has a high reputation, when it comes to furniture, for the following reasons:\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eDiversity: As a company with an extensive range, we are sure that you will find a perfect fit for any workspace.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSuperior Quality: Materials of great quality make our office tables last for ages.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAffordable Prices: Without a doubt, our pricing is competitive, which gives us a place in the market without compromising quality.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCustomer Support: Our team will assist you throughout the process, from the selection of the right Office furniture for professionals to installation, thus guaranteeing customer satisfaction.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eConclusion\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhether you are an entrepreneur, a remote worker, or a corporate manager, the proper office table is one of the foundations of a productive workspace. Here we have Damro providing matchless varieties of office tables for workspaces, combining functionality, durability, and style. Explore our collection today and find out how our office desks can elevate your workspace experience to new heights of productivity and professionalism.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Office Tables \u0026 Desks – Workstations | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/office-tables\",\n  \"description\": \"Browse Damro’s office table collection featuring compact workstations, executive desks, and conference tables designed for efficient and stylish workspace setups.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","topContent":"\u003ch2\u003eStudy and Computer Tables That Combine Comfort and Functionality\u003c/h2\u003e","hoverIcon":"","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","homeCategoryImg":"","regionCollection":[{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b184939960e7bbb","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Table.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/bangalore-office-tables1.jpg","regionId":"60ae18731e3fc640d831ab15","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b184969c90e7bbc","categoryspac