 Office Table.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/APTS (6).jpg","regionId":"639c65d4cfcaa1d9535e58ab","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b18494c600e7bc2","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Tableicon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/plp39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Kolkata (6).jpg","regionId":"63be9be757d1050bc75e9f02","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b18491a7e0e7bc3","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Tableicon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/plp39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Kolkata (6).jpg","regionId":"615c3fe80d4e6c3390fa260b","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b1849d0e60e7bc4","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Table.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Kolkata (6).jpg","regionId":"63bea35057d1059b1e5e9f13","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b1849042c0e7bc5","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Table.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Chennai (5).jpg","regionId":"63a152aecfcaa1c5e55e59f5","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b18491e680e7bc6","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Table.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/bangalore-office-tables1.jpg","regionId":"6364ee4e1b950054791eea65","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b184907510e7bc7","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Table.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/APTS (6).jpg","regionId":"639c58eacfcaa177515e586b","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b18495e1f0e7bc8","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Tableicon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/plp39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Kolkata (6).jpg","regionId":"63bea67957d105d8415e9f3a","offer":""},{"ourcollection":true,"categoryspace":false,"_id":"68da3c1d8b184966640e7bc9","categoryspaceimage":"","menuImage":"","icon":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/9 Office Tableicon.jpg","hoverIcon":"","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/plp39.jpg","homeCategoryImg":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/Raipur (6).jpg","regionId":"63beaa1c57d1055b9f5e9f5f","offer":""}],"categoryspace":null,"categoryspaceimage":"","offer":null},{"_id":"649540ea77c6ad5e84af318b","ourcollection":false,"trending":false,"enable":true,"name":"Conference Tables and Reception Counters ","description":"Enhance your office space with Damro’s premium range of conference tables and reception counters. Designed with sleek finishes and sturdy build quality, our furniture solutions bring professionalism and practicality to meetings, front desks, and client areas. Choose from various sizes and configurations to fit your workspace needs seamlessly.","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/40.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61aada4604b0430f2bbe5","icon":"","hoverIcon":"","slug":"conference-tables-and-reception-counter","lastUpdatedBy":"68c2c17ab37e84ff9f0b15ab","sortValue":3,"metaTitle":"Buy Reception Counters \u0026 Conference Tables upto 35 % off","metaDescription":"Get durable conference tables \u0026 reception counter solutions. Order reception counters or office reception table designs built for space and daily use.","metaKeywords":"conference tables, reception counters, office tables, meeting tables, office reception desks, commercial furniture, Damro office","createdAt":"2023-06-23T06:51:22.158Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T08:03:24.888Z","__v":0,"bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eCreate a Seamless Workspace with Elegant Conference Tables and Reception Counters\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eDesigning a workspace that balances professionalism and functionality starts with the right furniture. Durable conference tables and reception counters not only enhance the look of your office but also improve its efficiency. We here at Damro offer functional and stylish Conference Tables and Reception Counters for Your Business.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eConsider these points before buying\u003c/h3\u003e\u003ch4\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h4\u003e\u003ch4\u003eConference Tables for Offices\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eSize and Space: Firstly, measure your conference room and determine how big a table will fit in it. Then ensure that the table has enough space for chairs and movement.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSeating Capacity: Choose a table that fits the number of people that normally attend your meetings.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMaterial and Finish: Choose wood, metal, or glass depending on the style of your office and how you want the durability.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eTech Integration: Find tables that have built-in cable management and outlets for modern gadgets.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eReception Counters for Businesses\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eDesign and Look: The reception counter is the first point of contact for people. Choose a design on that reflects your brand image.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eFunctionality: Give space with ample storage and workspace to serve all requirements of your receptionist.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMaterial: Specify durable materials such as laminate, metal, or wood that can withstand everyday use.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAccessibility: Counters provided with ADA-compliant designs should be kept in mind so that all visitors can be served.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePoints to consider before buying Conference Tables\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eDimensions of the Product: Go through the detailed dimensions so that the furniture will be perfect in your space.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMaterial Specifications: Understand the material used in construction for durability and maintenance requirements.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCustomer Reviews: Go through the reviews and ratings to understand product quality and seller reliability.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eDelivery and Assembly Services: Check if the seller provides delivery and assembly services for an easy-cosy setup.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWhat Are the Options Available at Damro?\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eAt Damro, we offer a wide range of modern conference table designs for offices and reception counters for businesses to suit diverse needs and preferences.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch4\u003eConference Tables\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eModern Designs: Stylish and functional tables with sleek finishes and ergonomic designs.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCustomizable Sizes: Tables available in various dimensions to fit any room size, large conference tables for meetings etc.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eDurable Materials: Options include wood, metal, and tempered glass for long-lasting use.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eTech-Friendly Features: Built-in cable management systems and power modules.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch4\u003eReception Counters\u003c/h4\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eElegant Styles: Designs that make a lasting first impression on visitors.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAmple Storage: Counters with integrated drawers, shelves, and cabinets for organized storage, reception counters for small spaces etc\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kcf024-conference-table-m42m51-10361-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAura Conference Table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kcf024-conference-table-m42m51-10361-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e₹\u0026nbsp;16,700MRP ₹\u0026nbsp;18,590\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kcf024-conference-table-m42m51-10361-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e(10% 0ff)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e========================================\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kcf023-conference-table-m42m51-10360-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAccolade Conference Table\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kcf023-conference-table-m42m51-10360-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e₹\u0026nbsp;28,900MRP ₹\u0026nbsp;32,390\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kcf023-conference-table-m42m51-10360-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e(11% 0ff)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/kcf023-conference-table-m42m51-10360-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAvailable Online\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e==================================\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/krt008-reception-table-m62m41-9877-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVista Reception Counter\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/krt008-reception-table-m62m41-9877-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e₹\u0026nbsp;15,900MRP ₹\u0026nbsp;18,090\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/krt008-reception-table-m62m41-9877-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e(12% 0ff)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e=====================================\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/krt007-reception-table-m62m41-10052-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRustic Reception Counter\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/krt007-reception-table-m62m41-10052-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e₹\u0026nbsp;17,900MRP ₹\u0026nbsp;20,090\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/krt007-reception-table-m62m41-10052-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e(11% 0ff)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e==================================\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eWhy Choose Damro’s Conference Tables\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eDiverse Product Line-Up: Damro encompasses every type of furniture catered to an enterprise's different tastes all under the same roof.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eQuality Guaranty: All products are subjected to careful screening for strength and performance after manufacture.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAffordable Price: Made possible by competitive pricing concerning quality. Our price starts from 15,000 to 30,000 Rs.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eExpert Advice: Staff professionals guide you in the easy selection of appropriate furniture designed for an office.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eEasy Shopping: This should be online, with excellent detailed information about the products and very prompt delivery.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eConclusion\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eInvesting in the right conference tables for offices and affordable office reception furniture for businesses is crucial for creating a productive and welcoming workspace. At Damro, we understand the importance of blending style, functionality, and durability. Explore our wide range of options and make your office space stand out. Choose Damro for furniture solutions that combine quality and elegance.\u003c/p\u003e","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Conference Tables \u0026 Reception Counters | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/conference-tables-and-reception-counter\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s collection of professional conference tables and reception counters. Designed for modern office environments, combining utility, design, and durability.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_str