son\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Storage Cupboards \u0026 Cabinets | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/storage-cupboards\",\n  \"description\": \"Shop Damro’s storage cupboards and cabinets online. Ideal for decluttering and styling bedrooms, living rooms, or offices with smart storage solutions.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[]},{"_id":"60b61bc8a4604b0430f2bbec","name":"Chairs","slug":"chairs","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/43.jpg","icon":"https://damroimagesstaging.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/10 Chairs.jpg","description":"Elevate your interiors with Damro’s diverse chair collection. From ergonomic office seating and stylish dining chairs to cozy accent armchairs, our range combines design and comfort. Perfect for home, office, or lounge spaces, each chair is built to last and enhance your décor.","homeCategorImg":"","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Chairs – Dining, Office \u0026 Wooden Chairs | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/chairs\",\n  \"description\": \"Ex\n","menuImage":"","subcate2":[{"_id":"60b61c03a4604b0430f2bbed","name":"High Back Chairs","description":"Experience superior comfort and support with Damro’s High Back Chairs. Engineered for extended use, these chairs offer padded headrests, adjustable lumbar support, and durable upholstery—perfect for home offices or professional settings. Choose from sleek mesh or plush cushioned designs to match your workspace aesthetics.\n\n","image":"https://damroimages.blob.core.windows.net/damroimages/43.jpg","menuImage":"","level":2,"parentId":"60b61bc8a4604b0430f2bbec","ourcollection":false,"icon":"","categoryImage":"","sortValue":0,"trending":false,"createdAt":"2021-05-04T12:04:27.278Z","updatedAt":"2025-09-29T08:15:49.421Z","__v":0,"slug":"high-back-chairs","enable":true,"metaDescription":"Order a high back chair built for both work and rest. Pick modern high back chair models that combine height, support, and clean design.","metaKeywords":"high back chairs, ergonomic chairs, executive office chairs, swivel chairs, lumbar support chairs, Damro office furniture","metaTitle":"Buy luxury Modern High Back Chairs for Office \u0026 Home upto 30% off","seoMarkup":"\u003cscript type=\"application/ld+json\"\u003e\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"High Back Chairs | Damro\",\n  \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/high-back-chairs\",\n  \"description\": \"Explore Damro’s high back chairs designed for superior lumbar support and ergonomic comfort. Perfect for office or study room setups.\",\n  \"publisher\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Organization\",\n    \"name\": \"Damro Furniture\",\n    \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com\",\n    \"logo\": {\n      \"@type\": \"ImageObject\",\n      \"url\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/assets/logo.png\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"potentialAction\": {\n    \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n    \"target\": \"https://www.damroindia.com/search?query={search_term_string}\",\n    \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n  }\n}\n\u003c/script\u003e\n","bottomContent":"\u003ch3\u003eEnhance Comfort and Productivity with High Back Chairs\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eSelecting the right office furniture plays a pivotal role in ensuring comfort and productivity at work. Among the essential furniture pieces, high-back chairs for offices stand out as a popular choice. Whether you are setting up a home office or upgrading your workplace, ergonomic high-back office chairs offer unparalleled support and functionality. Let’s delve into the details of what makes these chairs a must-have and how to select the best option for your needs.\u003c/p\u003e\u003ch3\u003eFactors to Evaluate Before Purchasing\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eErgonomics: Ensure that the chair provides lumbar support, adjustable armrests, and a headrest to advocate a healthy posture.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMaterial: High-quality breathable fabric mesh should be used for the chairs. It must also be durable leather or cushioned fabric.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAdjustability: Chairs should have adjustable features like seat height, tilt mechanism, and recline angle for personalized comfort.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eRobustness: A chair with a sturdy frame and high weight capacity for lasting use.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eDesign: Choose a chair that can match your office design and provide functionality.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eSupport Features: Look for lumbar support features, a contoured backrest, comfortable office chairs with headrest and comfortable office chairs with headrests\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMobility: Smooth-rolling casters and a swivel base of chairs support mobility and make it easy to move about.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eBuild Quality: Get good chairs having a strong build so they can withstand daily use.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eBreathability: Chairs that have mesh backs enable airflow and thus they will keep you cool all the time during endless working hours.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eWeight and Size: The dimensions of a chair should ensure that its weight capacity fits the user's needs.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFactors to Know Before Buying Online\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eDetailed Specifications: Carefully review product dimensions, materials, and adjustability features.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eCustomer Reviews: Read user reviews to gauge the comfort and quality of the chair.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eAssembly Requirements: Check if the chair requires assembly and if tools or assistance are provided.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eReturn Policies: Familiarize yourself with return or exchange terms in case the product doesn’t meet your expectations.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eWarranty: Opt for chairs with a reliable warranty to ensure peace of mind and product support.\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eThe Options Available in Damro\u0026nbsp;\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eA wide collection of high-back chairs is available at Damro with superior flexibility to meet the specific needs of the customers. Ergonomic high-back executive chairs do leave a great mark on maximum comfort and maximum style.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cul\u003e\u003cli\u003eExecutive Designs: Sleek and sophisticated chairs perfect for managerial and executive roles.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eModern Styles: Contemporary designs with innovative features to match modern office spaces.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eFully Customizable Options: Chairs have adjustable seat height, armrests, and reclining features.\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eMade Using Durable Material: Sculpted from premium and finest materials such as leather, mesh, and high-density foam.\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u0026nbsp;\u003c/li\u003e\u003cli\u003eErgonomic High Back Office Chairs\u003c/li\u003e\u003c/ul\u003e\u003ch3\u003eDamro's top-rated high-back chairs\u0026nbsp;\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och014-executive-chair-blue-2851-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePico High Back Chair - Blue\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och014-executive-chair-blue-2851-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e₹\u0026nbsp;6,290MRP ₹\u0026nbsp;6,990\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och014-executive-chair-blue-2851-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e(10% 0ff)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och014-executive-chair-blue-2851-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAvailable Online\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e=======================================\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och019-executive-chair-black-2854-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eReaper High Back Chair - Black\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och019-executive-chair-black-2854-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e₹\u0026nbsp;6,390MRP ₹\u0026nbsp;8,790\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och019-executive-chair-black-2854-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e(27% 0ff)\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och019-executive-chair-black-2854-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAvailable Online\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e======================================\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och022-executive-chair-black-2855-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRoma High Back Chair - Black\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://stage.damroindia.com/och022-executive-chair-black-2855-Bengaluru\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003e₹\u0026nbsp;8,990MRP ₹\u0026nbsp;9,690\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u0