<script type="text/javascript" id="" charset="">(function(a,e,b,f,g,c,d){a[b]=a[b]||function(){(a[b].q=a[b].q||[]).push(arguments)};c=e.createElement(f);c.async=1;c.src="https://www.clarity.ms/tag/"+g+"?ref\x3dgtm2";d=e.getElementsByTagName(f)[0];d.parentNode.insertBefore(c,d)})(window,document,"clarity","script","lmnxoywtoz");</script><script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "FAQPage",
  "mainEntity": [{
    "@type": "Question",
    "name": "Why Corner Sofas Are Perfect For Small Living Rooms",
    "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "With growing urbanisation, smaller living spaces are becoming a part of our lives. However, we can still make them vibrant and add luxury with clever furniture ideas. Sofas, often form the centrepiece of the living area, the right choice for compact spaces would be corner sofas or sectional sofas. These perfectly fit in while allowing you to entertain your guests and not take up much space."
    }
  },{
    "@type": "Question",
    "name": "Benefits of corner sofas",
    "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Corner sofas fit into the corners of compact living spaces maximizing the floor space allowing you to fit in other small living room furniture. It also provides an open space for movement and is ideal for creating an illusion of space."
    }
  },{
    "@type": "Question",
    "name": "How to choose the best corner sofa for small living rooms",
    "acceptedAnswer": {
      "@type": "Answer",
      "text": "Know the size
Choosing a model that fits your space becomes vital without disrupting the visual balance. Having sectional corner sofas helps create a clean and organized look for compact spaces.

Style & design
You can find corner sofas in various sleek and contemporary designs suiting your living area with particular shades like neutral colours that make the room appear bigger."
    }
  }]
}
</script>
